name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo1_0

Why

Ay, equis

Do you want something

A hint then 
If you're gonna interrupt my day

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo1_22
text_en: Just trying to say hello, is all.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo1_23

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo1_24

text_en: You did better with the question about home

There

Nice for you

Other than that? 
I'll think

Doesn't matter

So why think about them

text_en: Anyone back home missing you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_46
text_en: O...kay... [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_47
text_en: Sometimes painful memories are all that get us through.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_48
text_en: We're talking on the *internet* and you know the *phone* exists, yeah?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_49
text_en:
¿Sí? 
What do you know of pain?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_50
text_en:
Bien podría ser un pinche fantasma 
Call from beyond the grave, can't change, can't live, can't die

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_51
text_en: Do you know what it feels like to get your head cut off? I do. I've died a thousand times. And it *hurts,* lady.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_52
text_en:
I did not ask you to 
I'm busy 
Vete

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_53
text_en: I don't have to prove myself to you, lady.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_54
text_en:
Touched by La Flaca 
Another fantasma like the rest of us 
Reliving their deaths again and again and again

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_55
text_en:
Sí 
There is family at home 
Better they think I am already dead

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_56
text_en: Do you take the pain for other people by choice, or because it's your duty?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_57
text_en: There's still life worth living, here.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo2_58
text_en: I don't think I like where this is going. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_59
text_en:
¿¡What are we?! 
FANTASMAS nothing more 
Like shadows on a VHS tape used one too many times

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_60
text_en:
No, better they think I am already dead 
I take this pain for them

text_en:
Both I suppose 
I chose a long time ago 
Now it's too late to go back

text_en:
Suure, suure 
With Amir's games and Arthur's drinking and Aoi's music and Quincy's pictures

Empty hobbies 
Empty souls 
Passing time through eternity

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_1044

I have work to do

Humility from our savior 
I like it

I have to get back to work

Babas 
Heads up

Yeah, yeah, hello, *good morning*

Need you to get more gauze 
Running low on supplies

text_en: Lo siento, right

text_en:
My newest corazoncito, my new rat 
She is still learning to behave

text_en: If I see any, I'll grab some.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo3_87

Gracias

text_en: You tell me

text_en: Huh?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo3_94
text_en: I don't think I like where this is going. [End.]

I want to know why you think I like rats

text_en: Because they're often neglected and misunderstood?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo3_99

text_en:
Ay, Lua, sálvame 
No

text_en: ¡JAJA!

text_en:
Humility from our savior 
I like it

text_en:

Gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_110
text_en:
Are there gods still 
Or have you forgotten them all

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_112
text_en: I'm sorry, back up, what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_113
text_en: You have a hell of a way of starting a conversation, you know that?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_114
text_en: Not touching THIS with a ten foot pole... [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_115
text_en: Haven't forgotten them, we didn't have any. I don't count the Orokin.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_116
text_en:
¿Neta, babas? 
The gods, babas - Sol and Lua 
Are they remembered?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_119
text_en: I... hate to break it to you, but Sol and Lua aren't gods. One's a star and the other is a rock that's seen some shit

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_120
text_en: They aren't worshipped as gods anymore, I'm sorry. But Lua is still considered kind of sacred.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_121
text_en: I can only speak for myself, and I was raised to worship the Orokin. And then I learned better.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_117
text_en:
Heh, sí 
You'll get used to it 
Or not

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_118
text_en:
Well? 
Are they still worshiped

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_122
text_en: Lárgate

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_123
text_en:
You didn't have gods... 
Who're the orokin?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_125
text_en: They were assholes who thought they were above everyone else. Enough said.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_126
text_en: They were a group of people who ruled over the Origin system. Who thought of themselves as gods.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_135
text_en:
Not the first time men dressed themselves as kings 
And thought themselves divine

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_136
text_en:
Won't be the last 
Talk to me more of them another time 
I have work to do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_124
text_en:
What do you mean 
Kind of sacred

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_127
text_en: Lua... well... It kind of got shoved in the void for a while.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_128
text_en: It's complicated. A really long story. The short of it is, it's still very important, but not worshiped.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_129
text_en:
If it is half like what it sounds 
You put her WHERE?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_130
text_en: The void is kind of like a non-dimension? It's sometimes black and white. It's weird. Kind of tingly.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_131
text_en: Whoa, back up. *I* didn't put her anywhere! I had nothing to do with it!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_133
text_en: I was abandoned on a space ship and then stuck in my own personal hell while all that nonsense was going on.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_134
text_en: Then what DO you worship

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_137
text_en: The universe. The void. Everything.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_138
text_en: Nothing.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_139
text_en: I believe in myself and the people around me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_140
text_en: It's personal.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_141
text_en:
Recognizing one is small in the face of everything is important 
I can respect that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_142
text_en:
Certainty in nothing is its own belief 
And anyone who tells you otherwise is a fool

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_143
text_en:
That's a motivational poster not a belief 
But whatever brings you peace at night

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_144
text_en: I respect that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_1687
text_en: Gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_145
text_en:
Sí 
This kingdom of death of yours
Tell me more

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_146
text_en:
Oh yeah 
And what was that "hell" like 
Did it burn?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_147
text_en: Duviri was an alternate dimension I kind of... created? Sort of? By existing?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_148
text_en: You're a weird lady...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_149
text_en: None of your business.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_150
text_en: No, that's one thing they didn't do to me, thankfully.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_151
text_en: It was made out of the void plucked from my mind and made real. Manifestations of a frightened child.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_152
text_en:
Mm 
Seen a lot of suffering 
Suppose it does that to you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_153
text_en:
You're right
It isn't

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_154
text_en: They?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_155
text_en: Dominus Thrax and his goons.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_156
text_en: They. Me. It's all the same. It's a long story.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_157
text_en:
The name means nothing to me 
I want to know his soul 
Who was this *they* that hurt you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_158
text_en:
In a way, I think I understand 
Circumstances are different 
But the pain's the same

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_159
text_en: He wasn't real. He was a fictional character the void plucked from my head and turned into reality by my sheer presence.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_160
text_en: Would you want to tell me all about *your* darkest moments right now?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_161
text_en: But it all went wrong when I grew up and wanted to leave. And they began killing me, again and again.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_162
text_en:
No, we are desconocidos 
Fair point
Another time, then

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_163
text_en: Maybe we have more in common than I gave you credit for, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_164
text_en:
Stories made real 
And La Flaca knows your face

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_111
text_en: Maybe we have more in common than I gave you credit for, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_889
text_en: I'm not kicking her out. Even if she's working for Entrati, it's not her fault. She's an animal being loyal to the owner who loves her. I can't be cruel to her.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_165
text_en:
These deaths you had 
Did they hurt?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_890
text_en:
Fine, sí 
That will be good enough 
But if she hurts one of my bebecitos 
It means war

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_166
text_en:
Tell me, babas 
Do you know much of death?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_856
text_en:
Esa gata, that freaky mutant cat 
Keeps looking at my panquecitos like they're lunch 
I don't like it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_167
text_en: And here I thought *I* was morbid...  Are you okay?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_168
text_en: LOL. Lady, don't get me started. You?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_169
text_en: You seriously need to get outside more often.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_170
text_en: La Flaca and I know each other well

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_171
text_en: Ay, equis

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_172
text_en: La Flaca is death?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_173
text_en: Who's La Flaca?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_174
text_en:
Sí 
Surprised you caught on

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_175
text_en:
The Skinny Lady 
Death

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_176
text_en:
I respect her 
Even if sometimes I don't want to like her 
But she shepherds the ones I care for

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_177
text_en: But you're a medic. Don't you heal people? How can you "respect" death?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_178
text_en: Death isn't a person. It's a thing that happens.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_179
text_en: Va

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_180
text_en: You're thinking about it all wrong

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_181
text_en:
All those times you died 
Do you blame her for ending your pain? 
Was it her fault you suffered or was it the ones who hurt you to blame

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_182
text_en:
My job is to make sure she takes people when it is their time 
Not until she rips them from my hands 
And not a damn second sooner

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_183
text_en:
But when she does come 
I make sure she knows she is welcome 
She takes away pain, babas 
She is not to be feared, but respected

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_184
text_en: When I was in Duviri, and I knew I was about to die, sometimes it was a relief to know it'd be over soon.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_185
text_en: I guess part of me understands that. Even if I don't like the idea of dying.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_186
text_en: I am... going to stop this conversation, now.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_187
text_en: Ay, equis, pansy

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_188
text_en: That no matter how badly it was about to hurt, the darkness would come and it'd be done.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_189
text_en:
¿Sí, see? 
You get it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_190
text_en: But I also knew I was going to come back.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_191
text_en: But I don't think it means everybody should die. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_192
text_en:
And for those with faith 
So are we 
Maybe not as literally as you jaja 
Though... now we are fantasmas, too

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_193
text_en:
That is why I heal 
To make sure La Flaca is certain in who she is taking 
And that she ONLY gets who she needs 
And no one else

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_194
text_en:
Caught in the same endless cycle as you were... 
Outside Mictlán embrace

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_195
text_en: We've all seen her sent loved ones too soon by the actions of others...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_196
text_en: Yeah.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo1_197
text_en: I could toast to that.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_198
text_en: Sí

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_199
text_en:
Been fun 
Back to work for me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo1_200
text_en: I need to go back to work

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_891
text_en:
AGGGHHHH 
Why did you have to put it like that 
Aaayyyyyyy babaaaas 
Fight fair!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_201
text_en: What're the names of your pet rats?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_202
text_en: How many pet rats do you have?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_203
text_en: Mm?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_204
text_en:
Mm? 
4

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_205
text_en: Vaquero, Anita, Neenah, and Tláloc

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_206
text_en: How did you pick their names?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_207
text_en: You should name one after me. :)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_208
text_en:
Vaquero means cowboy 
Anita is a friend back home 
Neenah was a friend who is gone now 
Tláloc after an ancient god of rain

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_209
text_en:
Heh 
Name it Babas 
Hope it doesn't start licking the wallpaper

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_210
text_en:
Tláloc is a *dick* 
The rat not the god jaja 
I don't need that kind of bad mojo

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_211
text_en: What *does* Babas mean, anyway?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_212
text_en: Har har. I know what that means, y'know.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_213
text_en: Good

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_214
text_en: I've never heard of Tláloc before. Did he come before Lua and Sol? Before dualism?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_215
text_en: What makes him a dick? lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_216
text_en:
Don't worry 
It could be worse

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_892
text_en:
No me gusta cuando te pasas de listo, babas 
Fine, FINE 
She stays but if she hurts one of my bebecitos 
It means war

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_217
text_en: Sí, long long ago, my people worshiped ancient gods, some of whom could be... bloody

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_218
text_en:
He likes to bite 
He's like the ancient people and their gods, some of whom could be... bloody

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_219
text_en: What do you mean, "bloody?"

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_220
text_en: Sounds, um, pleasant.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_221
text_en: Mkay... I trust you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_222
text_en: I don't believe you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_223
text_en: Bueno

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_224
text_en: No skin off my back

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_225
text_en: Xipe Totec, the Flayed One, who was the god of rebirth, of agriculture, and war

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_226
text_en: Flayed One...?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_227
text_en: He doesn't sound TOO bad...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_228
text_en:
In the yearly festival to celebrate him, war prisoners would be skinned, and bands of men would wear their flesh like their own and accept offerings from the people of the cities in his name 
Like I said 
They could be bloody from time to time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_229
text_en: Well. Thanks for the nightmare fuel.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo2_230
text_en: Humans are weird.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_231
text_en: De nada

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo2_232
text_en: Couldn't agree more

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_857
text_en: You mean Kalymos? I'll make sure she leaves your rats alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_233
text_en:
These orokin, Entrati was one 
Yeah? 
Makes sense, him thinking he's some kinda god, ruining lives

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_234
text_en:
I want to know where Entrati gets off 
Coming here and ruining lives 
Who does this pinche güey think he is?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_235
text_en: Kind of? Halfway. After his void experiments, they adored him. But he was bitter about how they treated him before, so... it's hard to explain.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_236
text_en: I gotta go, sorry. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_237
text_en: I think it's just how he is. You should meet the Cavia.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_238
text_en: But he thinks he's doing all this for the greater good.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_239
text_en: He's used to rubbing shoulders with the Orokin. He's used to thinking he's a god.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_240
text_en: I gotta go, sorry. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_241
text_en: Orokin?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_242
text_en: Who're the cavia

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_243
text_en: Greater good, my ass

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_244
text_en: Friends of mine. Animals that Entrati experimented on by sending them into the void.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_245
text_en: I dunno, your ass *is* pretty good. ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_246
text_en: Stopping the Man in the Wall is a pretty important problem, to be fair.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_247
text_en: The ruling class of people in the future I come from. They made people worship them as gods.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_248
text_en: They were assholes who thought they were above everyone else. Enough said.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_249
text_en:
As if I didn't need a reason to HATE him more... 
LAB ANIMALS?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_250
text_en:
Doesn't mean he's doing the right thing 
Pendejos like him are all the same 
Bullheadedly charging at their problem 
Everyone else is collateral damage

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_251
text_en:
Not the first time men dressed themselves as kings 
And thought themselves divine

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_256
text_en: They were sent into the void and came out with intelligence.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_252
text_en:
JAJA 
You know it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_253
text_en:
But pendejos like him are all the same 
Get their head set on fixing a problem and everyone else is just collateral damage 
They don't care who they hurt or how bad 
He'd burn the universe if it meant he got his way

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_254
text_en:
That explains Entrati 
He thinks he is god and acts accordingly
Pendejos like him are all the same 
Bullheadedly charging at their problem 
Everyone else is collateral damage

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_257
text_en: The void can do... weird things like that.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_258
text_en:
And let me guess, he just abandoned them 
Saw what he'd done and walked away because he didn't need them anymore

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_255
text_en:
He doesn't care who he hurts or how bad 
Everyone is just collateral damage to him in the name of his mission

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_259
text_en: Yep, you got it. Now they're a... bunch of traumatized animals with human intelligence.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_260
text_en: He's trying to stop the Man in the Wall. It's important.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_261
text_en:
Oh, pobres ángeles inocentes 
I would love them, you're right... 
We do not deserve animals 
Their love for us is pure and only asks for love in return

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_262
text_en:
Not saying it isn't 
But pendejos like him always do the worst things in the name of doing the ultimate good 
They don't care who they hurt or how bad, as long as they WIN and get their way

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_263
text_en: People like him get people like us murdered

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_264
text_en: I do everything I can to help the Cavia. Honestly, I prefer them to most people. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_265
text_en: Maybe I can take you to see them someday.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_266
text_en:
I would adore that 
Gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_267
text_en:
You'll never see HIM die for his cause 
He'll never sacrifice HIS life 
Just the ones around him

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_268
text_en: Makes you wonder which one the monster is in the end

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_269
text_en: I get why he'd do anything to stop the Man in the Wall.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_270
text_en: In order to stop the Man in the Wall, we need him. But that doesn't mean I trust him. Or like him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_271
text_en:
That's why I keep pets 
My rats keep me company when I'm lonely 
When I can't stand people, they're there 
Sweet little souls, just wanting love

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_272
text_en:
Do not pretend to understand the gods 
They are beyond us and it is stupid to think otherwise

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_273
text_en:
Good 
Don't turn your back on that pendejo 
But be careful that you don't pretend to know the nature of the gods

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_274
text_en:
And cheddar crowns jaja 
But mostly love

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_275
text_en:
But if I ever meet Entrati again 
I am going to make him HURT 
I am going to make him pay for every ounce of pain he paid those animals 
And I am going to make sure he knows why

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_276
text_en: I'll be there to help you do it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_277
text_en: Once the Man in the Wall is dealt with, he's all yours.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_278
text_en:
Xipe Totec would be proud 
But like the Flayed One, be careful this old god of yours does not wear your face next

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_279
text_en:
This THING he's chasing after 
It wears human skin like the ancient bloody gods of old

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_280
text_en:
Xipe Totec the Flayed One would wear the skin of his enemies 
And so does your Man in the Wall

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_281
text_en:
Or maybe you can hold him down 
Heh, here I am getting all excited about something that'll never happen

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_282
text_en:
So be careful what you do 
Or else it might wear your face next
¿Yeah, babas?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_858
text_en: Kalymos won't hurt your rats.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_283
text_en:
I should go back to work 
Nos vemos

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_859
text_en:
No 
That thing is entrati's pet not yours 
It does his bidding 
It looks at me just like he did

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_284
text_en: I might be a tiny bit sad

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_285
text_en: D'aw, thanks.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo3_286
text_en: Love you too, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_287
text_en:
I should go back to work 
Nos vemos, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_288
text_en:
Muah 
I should go back to work 
Nos vemos, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_860
text_en:
¿Sí? 
How are you so sure? 
That thing is entrati's pet not yours 
It does his bidding 
It looks at me just like he did

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_289
text_en:
Hey, babas 
I have another small favor to ask you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_290
text_en:
Hey, babas 
I have a small favor to ask you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_291
text_en: Sure. What's up?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_292
text_en: Y'know I'm not your little bitch, right?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_293
text_en: Run your own errands. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_294
text_en:
Sí 
I bet I could make you beg for treats 
But you're probably too soft for that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_295
text_en: Are... you threatening me or hitting on me?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_296
text_en: Bring it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_297
text_en:
¿Por qué no ambos? 
Don't distract me, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_298
text_en:
Cuidadito, babas 
Don't distract me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_299
text_en:
I have too much work to do to play games and run around 
These civvies collect bullet wounds like Amir collects computers

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_300
text_en:
Point being, medkits 
I need more 
Find them or buy them, don't care 
Get them to me 
Te lo agradecería mucho

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_861
text_en: And how does she look at you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_301
text_en: I'm on it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_302
text_en: No promises.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo4_303
text_en: Get them yourself.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_304
text_en: None asked for

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_305
text_en: Gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_862
text_en: She's a kavat, Lettie, not a person.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieBirthdayConvo_165
text_en: Happy Birthday! On Star Days no less. How Romantic. :)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieBirthdayConvo_166
text_en: Hey! Happy Birthday! Did your rats get you anything?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_863
text_en:
Like she's trying to figure out how to eat ME 
Like a person 
Like one of those cavia you told me about 
With too much intelligence behind those eyes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_864
text_en:
Like a person 
Like she's trying to figure out how to eat ME 
With too much intelligence behind those eyes 
Does the future have smart animals?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_306
text_en: So... what's your problem with Eleanor, anyway?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_865
text_en:
Are you so sure 
Esa gata, it seems too smart to me 
Looks at me with human intelligence 
Does the future have smart animals?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_307
text_en: I think you need to cut Eleanor some slack.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_308
text_en: [Ignore.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_309
text_en:
We all wound up as monsters 
But that bruja delights in what we've become 
Gets a sick glee out of messing about in my head 
Sees too much and thinks she knows everything

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_310
text_en:
¿Ay, sí? 
And why is that? 
Did the bruja send you to talk to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_311
text_en:
Even if she never devolves into the Techrot 
And she stays like she is now I don't care 
That bruja still enjoys this shit too much

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_312
text_en: No, she didn't. I'm here on my own accord.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_313
text_en: It doesn't matter if she did or not, I still think you should ease up.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_314
text_en:
And why should I 
She could snap at any point and devolve into the Techrot 
And even if she doesn't that bruja enjoys all this too much 
We're all monsters now but the difference is she LIKES it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_315
text_en: Just because she embraces what's happened to her doesn't make her a bad person.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_316
text_en: I just don't think you're being fair to her, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_317
text_en:
It's one thing to accept it 
It's another thing to enjoy it 
And she can learn to not be a metiche and stay the hell out of my DAMN head

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_318
text_en:
¿Ay, sí, verdad? 
Do tell

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_319
text_en: She's one of your teammates, Lettie. And like it or not, you're stuck with her. You need to work on letting go of your grudges.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_320
text_en: She's lost her voice. She has to listen to everybody's thoughts all the time. She gets weird flashes of things she doesn't understand.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_321
text_en:
Sure, sure 
How well is that working out for you, babas 
Have you forgiven all your grudges

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_322
text_en: And she's the one who is the closest to the Techrot. Can you imagine what that must feel like, to hear them all the time?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_323
text_en: And she has all of YOU treating her like she's the real monster. Can you imagine what that must feel like?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_324
text_en: Can you blame her for meeting that kind of disgust with defiance instead of shame?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_325
text_en:
Against your Xipe Totec and all the terrible things your void god has done 
You tell me you have no grudges 
Pendejadas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_326
text_en:
Against Entrati and the Orokin and what they did to you 
You tell me you have no grudges 
Pendejadas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_327
text_en:
Against Duviri and the place that hurt you so many times 
You tell me you have no grudges

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_328
text_en:
Your life has been nothing but dancing with La Flaca and you tell me you have no grudges 
Pendejadas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_866
text_en:
Are you so sure 
You told me about the cavia 
Those poor animals that cabrón gave intelligence to and abandoned?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_329
text_en: You're right, I still hold grudges. I'm not perfect. All I'm saying is that you're treating her like she's a monster. Can you blame her for meeting disgust with defiance?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo5_330
text_en: You're right, I still hold grudges. I'm not perfect. All I'm saying is that she's the one who is the closest to the Techrot. Can you imagine what that must feel like, to hear them all the time?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_331
text_en:
That is exactly the problem 
You keep making my arguments for me, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_332
text_en:
Mierda... 
I do not like her in my head, babas 
But when you put it like that... no I do not blame her 
It is how I would handle it, too

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_333
text_en:
I tell you what 
You have the bruja metiche work on staying out of my head 
And... I will work on cutting her some slack, ¿sí?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_334
text_en:
Someday they will wear her skin like your Xipe Totec wears the Major 
And you will be gone and not be able to save her

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_335
text_en:
Someday they will consume her 
And you will be gone and not be able to save her

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo5_336
text_en:
Vete 
Go away 
Too much to do to waste time on this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_867
text_en:
Those poor animals that cabrón gave intelligence to and abandoned?! 
How do you know she isn't one, too?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_337
text_en: Hey Lettie, I have a favor to ask you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_338
text_en: Hey Lettie, what do you think about tabletop roleplaying games?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_339
text_en:
You've been helping me 
So I suppose I'll hear you out 
What is it, babas?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_340
text_en: Are you bleeding to death?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_341
text_en: I know this'll sound like a massive waste of time, but Amir wants to get us all to play a game with him called Fables & Frontiers.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_342
text_en: Estás bromeando, ¿verdad?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_343
text_en: Lárgate

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_344
text_en: Amir really wants us all to play Fables & Frontiers with him. It's really important to him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_345
text_en: Why do I get the feeling I'm about to be?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_347
text_en:
You're right 
It does sound like a massive waste of time 
And like pulling my own teeth out with a pair of rusty pliers

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_348
text_en:
Because someone else IS right now 
Is what you want ACTUALLY important?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_349
text_en:
And while there's pain that I enjoy 
That's not it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_350
text_en: You owe me a favor, though.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_351
text_en: I... wait. What about pain?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_352
text_en: It is to Amir.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_353
text_en: Because you aren't stupid

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_354
text_en: Is what you want ACTUALLY important?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_355
text_en: It's not a matter of life and death, so. No. It can wait.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_356
text_en:
What that escuincle thinks is important and what IS important are very different 
I do not have time for this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_357
text_en: Bueno

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_358
text_en:
Heh 
Don't get too excited babas 
Te queda grande la yegua

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_359
text_en:
I do 
You're calling it in for a silly child's game of make believe?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_360
text_en: Mm... Never mind. I'll save it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank2Convo6_361
text_en: I am. It's worth it, this means a lot to Amir.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_362
text_en:
Suit yourself, babas... 
I'll play this stupid game 
But only AFTER the work day 
Now vete

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo6_363
text_en:
Smart choice, babas 
Now vete

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_868
text_en: There are the Cavia, who are these lab animals that were sent into the Void and came out intelligent. Well.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_364
text_en:
How do you do it, babas 
No entiendo

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_365
text_en: You forgot to tell me what you're talking about.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_366
text_en: Do what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_367
text_en: Magic.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_368
text_en: Ay, equis

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_369
text_en:
Jaja, sí 
Lo siento, too much time in my head alone 
Though less so recently between you and the bruja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_370
text_en:
Being trapped for centuries without time 
Without change, without movement 
We are fantasmas haunting this place

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_371
text_en:
You say you've done it in Duviri 
That Kingdom of Death and Stories 
Yo me habría vuelto loca 
I'm worried I will lose my mind, now

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_372
text_en:
You say you've done it before 
In this other land of yours 
Yo me habría vuelto loca 
I'm worried I will lose my mind, now

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_373
text_en: Honestly? I almost did. I chose to go numb instead.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_374
text_en: I... think I did lose my mind for a little while. I don't remember whole chunks of it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_375
text_en: What happened to me in Duviri is very different to what's happening here. You're not alone like i was.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_376
text_en:
¿Sí? 
Numb, an empty shell 
But you came back to life it seems, I don't see that in you now

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_377
text_en:
I've seen that in soldiers after bad battles, blocking it all out 
The mind protects itself from the worst sometimes 
It's for the best, babas, trust me 
Well? How did you survive?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_378
text_en:
Sí, cómo no 
Not the people I'd want to spend eternity with, babas 
No offense, look around

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_379
text_en: Once I realized what was happening, I fought like hell to keep from letting it consume me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_380
text_en: I had help from friends to pull me out of it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_381
text_en:
I was only around to stitch them back together, before we were turned into monsters 
Now we don't have a choice 
You think they want me here?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_382
text_en:
But you cannot fight eternity 
You escaped that place 
I don't see a way out for us... do you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_383
text_en:
Bueno, I'm screwed then 
Jaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_869
text_en: Yes, but - oh, this is going to piss you off already, I can tell.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_384
text_en: Well, *I* like you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_385
text_en: You think the other Hex don't like you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_386
text_en: Well, you aren't exactly "approachable," Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_387
text_en: Well, maybe if you weren't so bitchy...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_388
text_en: No... I don't, I'm sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_389
text_en: I mean, I can take you out of here via transference for short periods.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_390
text_en:
Appreciate the honesty 
I guess we take bets on who goes crazy first

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_391
text_en:
¿Ay, Sí? 
¿Want to take me out for a walk? 
Cuidadito, I am not going to be the pet of this relationship... 
¡Yo no me dejo!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_392
text_en:
Who knows 
Might be me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_393
text_en: Challenge accepted.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_394
text_en: Are... you hitting on me?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_395
text_en:
¿Ay, Sí? 
Just how much do you like me, babas 
I've been wondering how quickly you'd break

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_396
text_en:
Eh, know me well enough 
But we are not close 
Except maybe me and Arthur

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_397
text_en: You think I don't know that, babas?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_398
text_en:
JAJAJA 
If I weren't I wouldn't be Lettie anymore 
I am who I am babas 
Take it or leave it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_399
text_en: I was just trying to be nice. You're not my type.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_400
text_en: Why don't you let people get close?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_401
text_en: You're afraid to trust people.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_402
text_en: You don't want to get hurt if you lose them.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_403
text_en:
Because I choose not to 
Because I've learned better 
It's safer this way for everybody

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_404
text_en: Lárgate de aqui

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_405
text_en:
¡No manches, babas! 
Do you know how long rats live? 
2-3 years at most 
I am used to losing my little panquecitos

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_406
text_en:
And I love them more than humans 
I am comfortable with grief and loss, more than you know 
Do not pretend you know me babas 
Lárgate

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_407
text_en:
No manches, babas... 
Do you want me to be?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_408
text_en: Yeah, you're my type. I like to live dangerously. ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_409
text_en: No, I'd rather just stay friends.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_870
text_en: How do you know she isn't one, too?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_410
text_en: Just as a warning, I'm really stubborn, and I want to get to know you better.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_411
text_en: Thanks for the heads up. I won't take it personally if you step all over my feelings.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_412
text_en:
We'll see, babas, we'll see 
But I'll take you up on the offer for temporary freedom 
Maybe some fresh air from time to time is all this fantasma needs

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_413
text_en:
Fair 
But I'll take you up on the offer for temporary freedom 
Maybe some fresh air from time to time is all this fantasma needs

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_414
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Someone like you would need to be to survive 
Maybe that's your secret 
I like the stubborn ones, though 
They're harder to break

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_415
text_en:
Jaja 
It's not your feelings I want to step on

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_416
text_en: Challenge accepted.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_417
text_en: Are... you hitting on me?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_418
text_en: I just want to be your friend, Lettie. No offense.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_419
text_en:
¡No manches, babas! 
Do you want me to be?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_420
text_en: Yeah, you're my type. I like to live dangerously. ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo1_421
text_en: No, I'd rather just stay friends.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_422
text_en:
Jaja we'll see, babas 
We'll see

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo1_423
text_en:
Jaja, none taken 
Sí, friends is fine by me 
That's more than enough for most people

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_871
text_en:
LAB ANIMALS?! 
And let me guess 
Entrati is the one who tortured them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieTrust_424
text_en: Yeah, Lettie?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieTrust_425
text_en: babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieTrust_426
text_en: [Ignore.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieTrust_427
text_en: Uh... ¿Sí?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieTrust_428
text_en:
Gonna set one thing straight 
I'm not a cobarde 
I'm no stinking coward
But... you were right about one thing

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieTrust_429
text_en:
I don't trust people 
Plain and simple 
¿Entendiste?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieTrust_430
text_en: Understood.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieTrust_431
text_en: Not even me? Or the Hex?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieTrust_432
text_en:
Jaja 
Oh, babas 
You do make me smile when I need it 
I'll give you that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieTrust_433
text_en: Bueno

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_872
text_en:
¿Ay, sí? 
Does it have to do with entrati?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_873
text_en: Yeah.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_434
text_en:
Give me a reason not to hate Entrati 
And the whole damn future you come from

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_874
text_en: You guessed it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_435
text_en:
Because as far as I can tell 
He's an animal abusing cabrón 
And your whole stinking future can get screwed as far as I'm concerned

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_436
text_en:
And none of this "greater good" pendejadas 
And your whole stinking future can get screwed as far as I'm concerned

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_437
text_en:
Because from where I sit 
That cabrón thinks he is a god and he let one loose 
And now it's all our problems to deal with 
So him and his future can get screwed as far as I'm concerned

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_438
text_en: I don't disagree. I hate Entrati as much as you do. But the future is worth fighting for, even if it'd be better without him in it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_439
text_en: Entrati isn't all bad, he's trying to fix his mistakes. And anybody who's capable of love has something worth saving in them, IMO.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_440
text_en: Yikes. I know when a conversation is going to go poorly. I'm out. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_441
text_en:
Love? 
Who could possibly love someone like that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_442
text_en: His name's Loid. Sort of a... workplace romance, you could say.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_443
text_en: He had a family. Wife, kids, grandkids now.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_444
text_en:
¿Ay, sí? 
I did not see Loid here with him

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_445
text_en:
You said HAD 
What do you mean, HAD

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_446
text_en: Loid is still in the future, guarding Entrati's lab. He's been there for centuries.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_447
text_en: Entrati abandoned Loid like he abandons everybody.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_448
text_en: Well, the issue is, his daughter thinks he's lost, and is searching for him. It's complicated.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_449
text_en: I mean, I'm sure he loved them at one point...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_450
text_en: I've got a warning light going off in - um - I have to go. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_451
text_en:
Used and tossed away 
I bet not the first time he's done it 
¿Verdad?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_452
text_en:
He abandoned his family 
Let me guess 
He's done it another time hasn't he

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_453
text_en: Yeah... he abandoned the Cavia, the animals he experimented on and accidentally made intelligent.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_454
text_en: Yeah... he abandoned his family. He had a wife, kids, and now grandkids.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_455
text_en: Look, it doesn't matter. He doesn't define the future.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_456
text_en: Yeah... he abandoned Loid, his manservant he has a relationship with.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_457
text_en:
But he HAS defined it don't you see 
It's because of him that everything is the way it is

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_458
text_en:
?!?!?!??! 
If I ever see him again- 
I am going to KILL him, and let you reset the world so I can do it AGAIN

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_459
text_en:
You are making my point, ¿no? 
He is trash and the future is trash

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_460
text_en:
He is TRASH 
And the future is TRASH

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_461
text_en: I'm from the future. Do you think I'm trash?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_462
text_en: Just because you hate one guy doesn't mean the whole future is garbage.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_463
text_en:
it may not be ugly to you 
But it is WRONG 
It is not what the gods intended 
He tampered with it all

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_464
text_en: If he never angered Xipe Totec, this Man in the Wall, none of your future would exist

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_465
text_en: If he never unleashed this Man in the Wall, none of your future would exist

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_466
text_en:
The void would not have been unleashed, ¿no? 
Duviri would never have been made 
Your life would have been happier

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_467
text_en:
The void would not have been unleashed, ¿no? 
You never would have been trapped 
Your life would have been happier

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_468
text_en: There's no way of knowing what could have been. In fact, without the Tenno, all of humanity might be gone by now, wiped out by the Sentients.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_469
text_en: You're right, but I can't change what's been done. Not at that scale. I'm doing my best to save who and what I can.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_470
text_en: Sentients?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_471
text_en:
Sí
I am just angry, lo siento 
This is not your fault and you are not garbage

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_472
text_en:
You are like me 
Just a medic keeping as many lives from joining La Flaca too early as possible

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_473
text_en: A synthetic race made by the Orokin and the future human society to terraform a planet called Tau, because we were ruining Earth.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_474
text_en: A synthetic race made by the Orokin and future human society who waged war on us after they were made.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_475
text_en: But Entrati can go screw a brick sideways

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_476
text_en:
More mortals playing at being gods 
These orokin are trash 
The sentients lashed out at their creators

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_477
text_en: Why?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_478
text_en: Because the Orokin sent them there to terraform a new planet, Tau, and the Sentients were worried that we'd ruin that one, too.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_479
text_en: Because they're just as egotistical, violent, and evil as the Orokin.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_480
text_en:
More mortals playing at being gods 
These orokin are trash 
All that power and technology 
And they could not save our planet

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_481
text_en:
De tal palo, tal astilla 
Humans making a race in their image 
Thinking they are the Father and Mother
Disgusting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_482
text_en:
Instead they wanted to make a golden new home somewhere else 
Where they could be the only gods, far away from the Father and Mother

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_483
text_en: Father and Mother? You mean Sol and Lua?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_484
text_en: Sol and Lua aren't gods, Lettie... they're just a star and a rock...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_485
text_en:
Sí 
They are something special, deep down, something more to us than just what they are at first glance

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_486
text_en:
Sí 
And your Man in the Wall is just a collection of atoms 
And you are just a person with nothing special about them except what was done to them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_487
text_en:
Do you believe in the unseen, ¿babas? 
Do you believe in something beyond the world we can measure?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_488
text_en: I've told you already, I don't believe in anything.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_489
text_en: No. If you can't measure it, it doesn't exist.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_490
text_en: Maybe? I think it's just science we don't understand yet.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo2_491
text_en: Of course I do. I'm a product of the Void.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_492
text_en:
I feel sad for you 
Thinking you know everything there is to know 
How small your world must feel

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_493
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Don't think I disagree 
You know what we do not know and admit it 
I like that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo2_494
text_en:
Ay, sí
You are touched by the unseen more than most 
For better or worse

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_495
text_en:
Before all this nonsense 
Where did you come from, ¿babas?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_496
text_en: The nonsense started pretty early. Do you mean pre-Now, pre-Duviri, or Pre-Zariman?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_1690
text_en: Transference will finally be good for something, eh

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_498
text_en: Sorry, can't chat. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_499
text_en:
Jajaja 
You're right it did start early 
But where do you FEEL like you come from

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo4_1691
text_en: Bueno

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_501
text_en: Duviri, I guess.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_502
text_en: The Zariman, I guess.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_503
text_en: You're going to laugh at me... but this is the closest to a "home" as I've ever felt I've had.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_504
text_en: I don't really "come from" anywhere.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_505
text_en: Honestly? I... don't know. The Orokin kind of erased most of Ancient Earth's records. So I have no way of knowing how far in the future exactly I'm from.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_506
text_en: Despite what it did to you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_507
text_en:
That's the ship, ¿no? 
Isn't it abandoned now?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_508
text_en: Why do you think I would laugh at you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_509
text_en:
Sí, you who wanders 
Who has no home

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_510
text_en:
It must be hard 
To feel like you come from no place and no time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_511
text_en: We don't get to pick what our homes have done to us, sometimes.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_512
text_en: What it did to me, I did to myself. Just nightmares playing over and over again in my head.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_513
text_en: That's... a complicated question. It has its own ghosts.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_514
text_en: No, it's not abandoned. It has memories of people who call it home.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_515
text_en:
My family moved a lot then I joined the army 
Then with the ICR I fit in with no one and nowhere 
So I understand, in a way, feeling displaced

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_516
text_en:
Sí, don't I know that well 
My family moved a lot then I joined the army 
Then with the ICR I fit in with no one and nowhere

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_517
text_en:
But my home has not done to me what that place has done to you, babas 
I respect you for still thinking of it as where you come from

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_518
text_en: It's the place I know the most, and the place that knows me the most, I suppose.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_519
text_en:
But I have a people and a culture I can call my own 
Even if they are far away

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_520
text_en: My other option is Duviri and... no. My history with that place is... too complicated.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_521
text_en: My other option is the Zariman and it's not any kinder. It's filled with just as many ghosts and nightmares. Except there, more people than JUST me died.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_522
text_en:
More fantasmas, more death that follows you 
And I thought I knew La Flaca well

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_523
text_en:
Sí, something to be said for the familiar 
I suppose in time this place will feel like home for me 
Mierda, I hope that is a long time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_524
text_en: You're tough. You'll be fine.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_525
text_en: Hey. At least you have better company than I did.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_526
text_en: She's got me on speed dial.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_527
text_en: Ghosts follow me wherever I go. Sometimes I wonder if I'm just a ghost myself.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_528
text_en: How does my being haunted bring you hope?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_529
text_en: Pues, a ver

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_530
text_en:
Maybe 
You give me hope in that, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_531
text_en:
Jaja seems it 
But your ghosts give me hope

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_532
text_en:
Poor haunted babas 
But you give me hope

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_533
text_en: I'm glad my suffering brings you joy.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_534
text_en:
JAJA 
No, pequeño babas 
You can still smile

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_535
text_en:
Oh, babas, don't worry 
We would take turns

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_536
text_en: What?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_537
text_en: I - Oh. *Oh.* Heh. Well.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo3_538
text_en: I... don't like you like that, I'm sorry, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_539
text_en:
... You'll figure it out 
I have faith 
But this is not about your suffering 
Not today

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_540
text_en:
But this is not about your suffering 
Not today

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_541
text_en:
Lo siento, just playing around 
Won't happen again 
Besides, this is not about your suffering

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_542
text_en:
I see you with the other hex 
I see you laughing and finding happiness 
You are a fantasma, like me, like us 
But you still find MEANING

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo3_543
text_en:
There is hope in that 
And I will take what little I can get 
Gracias, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_875
text_en:
Then you're right 
It will piss me off 
But tell me anyway

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_544
text_en: So, where's home for you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_545
text_en: How'd you end up joining the Hex, Lettie?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_546
text_en:
Tenochtitlán City, originally 
But we moved to Libertatia when I was young 
You wouldn't know where either place is 
Big sprawling place overseas from here

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_547
text_en:
Same as most of the others 
I was in the ICR with Aoi, Arthur, and Quincy 
Everybody needs a medic to glue their ass back together when it gets an extra hole

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_548
text_en: How do you get on with Aoi?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_549
text_en: I'm surprised you can put up with Quincy. You don't seem to have a lot of patience.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_550
text_en: Have you found the hole where Arthur keeps the stick he's lodged up there?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_551
text_en: ICR?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_552
text_en:
Aoi has to learn when to care for Aoi 
Shit, she spends more time babying people than I do Not everybody needs their hand held 
Not everybody wants it either

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_553
text_en:
That boy and his games, I've seen them a thousand times 
They don't bother me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_554
text_en:
Jajaja 
Nah, it's the only thing keeping him standing 
Man like him is only upright because he's got souls to protect

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_555
text_en:
International Crisis Response 
Humanitarian gig 
Thought it'd be better than working for some mercenary force or army 
Shit, was I wrong

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_876
text_en: LAB ANIMALS?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_556
text_en: Do you have family missing you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_557
text_en:
How about you, babas 
Where do you call your home

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_558
text_en:
Doesn't matter 
Can't leave this cuchitril 
So why think about them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_559
text_en:
She burns herself out that way 
Happened before, it'll happen again 
Makes herself sick over it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_560
text_en:
He has a good heart 
Even better aim 
And knows how to keep his ass out of trouble 
That's all I need in a squadmate

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_561
text_en: How'd you meet Arthur?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_562
text_en: Why Höllvania, though?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_563
text_en:
It's a long story 
Short of it is

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_564
text_en:
Wasn't the place, it was the person I followed 
Arthur's why I'm here and in the ICR in the first place

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_565
text_en: This Duviri of yours?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_566
text_en:
Or is the hint in your name? 
You have no home

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_567
text_en:
Bien podría ser un pinche fantasma 
Call from beyond the grave, can't change, can't live, can't die
