name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_568
text_en: Sometimes painful memories are all that get us through.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_569
text_en: We're talking on the *internet* and you know the *phone* exists, yeah?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_570
text_en: Ok, well... never mind. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_571
text_en:
¿Sí? 
What do you know of pain?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_572
text_en: This place isn't so bad. Maybe I'll make this my home.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_573
text_en: Thanks for rubbing it in.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_574
text_en: I make my home wherever I am.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_575
text_en:
I have to get back to work 
Don't have much time for chismes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_576
text_en:
I decided a long time ago to follow him to the ends of the earth 
And I guess I'm stuck with that choice now, eh

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_577
text_en:
What are we?! 
FANTASMAS nothing more 
Like shadows on a VHS tape used one too many times

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_877
text_en: He took these lab animals and sent them into the Void. They came out with the intelligence of people - it nearly killed them. They're called the Cavia.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_578
text_en:
¿Ah, sí? 
Why is that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_579
text_en:
Mm 
It's what I do 
You'll adjust

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_580
text_en:
Like mi padre 
Always on deployment

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_581
text_en: Do you know what it feels like to get your head cut off? I do. I've died a thousand times. And it *hurts,* lady.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_1724
text_en: But I was in Duviri, dying repeatedly, when the Lotus decided to put Lua in the Void.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_583
text_en: You. ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_584
text_en: The company.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_585
text_en: The food.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_586
text_en:
Or not 
I don't care

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_587
text_en:
Well 
Don't let us stop you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_588
text_en:
Good question, babas 
See? 
Stick to the interesting ones 
They get you somewhere

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_589
text_en:
Good question, babas 
Stick to the interesting ones 
They get you somewhere

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_590
text_en:
Touched by La Flaca 
Another fantasma like the rest of us 
Reliving their deaths again and again and again

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_591
text_en:
No, better they think I am already dead 
I take this pain for them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_592
text_en:
Yeah, there is family at home
Better they think I am already dead
I will carry this pain for them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_593
text_en: Do you take the pain for other people by choice, or because it's your duty?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo4_594
text_en: There's still life worth living, here.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_595
text_en:
Jaja 
Oh really 
Ten cuidado con lo que deseas 
But if that's your flavor, so be it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_596
text_en:
Sí 
Because we're all a bucket of joy 
But everything's relative I suppose 
Still, why you don't leave blows my mind

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_597
text_en:
Every time I try to stop someone from making stupid decisions it never works 
Don't expect it to work now 
So I won't waste my time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_598
text_en:
Go on now 
Leave Mamá Lettie to her real work

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_599
text_en:
Both I suppose 
I chose a long time ago 
Now it's too late to go back

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_600
text_en:
Suure, suure 
With Amir's games and Arthur's drinking and Aoi's music and Quincy's pictures

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_601
text_en:
Empty hobbies 
Empty souls 
Passing time through eternity

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_602
text_en: I have work to do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_603
text_en:
I have work to do 
Vete

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_878
text_en:
I AM GOING to make that cabrón HURT 
Next time I see him I will torture him like he tortured those poor angelitos 
And he will NOT like it, I PROMISE you THAT

text_en: You holding up okay?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_605
text_en: How's it going with the civilians?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_606
text_en: [Ignore.]

text_en:
Mm? 
Like a revolving door jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_608
text_en:
Eh? 
All right I suppose 
Civvies are the same everywhere you get used to it in time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_609
text_en:
Even before you sometimes I feel like people come THROUGH me 
Just a face in an ICR tent wrapping wounds 
But I'm part of the building

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_610
text_en: Yeah, but it's still gotta be exhausting.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_611
text_en: Get used to what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_612
text_en:
I'm tough 
I am going nowhere 
Pero... Estoy muerta 
Not enough coffee in the world sometimes, ¿no?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_613
text_en:
Sí, you have no idea 
Not enough coffee in the world sometimes, ¿no? 
Pero, soy dura de roer 
I am going nowhere

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_614
text_en:
Their vacant stares and numb pain 
To them I'm a face in an ICR tent wrapping wounds 
I feel like people come THROUGH me like a revolving door 
And this was before YOU made it literal jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_615
text_en: Just because you're the tough one doesn't mean I can't care.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_616
text_en: Yeah but a steady stream of coffee doesn't hurt. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_617
text_en: I mean, what were you expecting from people who just lost everything?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_618
text_en: I can see why all the people turn into a blur after a while.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_619
text_en: At least you're a really sexy door. :P

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_620
text_en:
Sí,
It's enough to know someone has my back 
Arthur is like that 
Doesn't hover like Aoi, pretending to be mi mamá 
Just hands me a cup and says, you good?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_621
text_en:
Jajaja no it does not 
Arthur is like that 
Doesn't hover like Aoi, pretending to be mi mamá 
Just hands me a cup and says, you good?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_622
text_en:
Not their fault 
Not my fault either, babas 
Just tired of it all

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_623
text_en:
Sí, it isn't their fault there is always more of them 
Always thought it was never ending 
Now I know it really will never end 
Lua, sálvame

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_624
text_en:
JAJA 
Oh, babas, you know how to cheer up a lady 
Put that on my grave 
"Aquí yace la puerta más sexy que hayas visto."

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_625
text_en:
I like that question, babas 
Keep asking it 
Might need it from time to time 
And a cup or two of coffee won't hurt either

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_626
text_en:
Hablando de 
Back to work

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_627
text_en:
Hablando de 
Back to work 
Thanks for the distraction

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_628
text_en:
Gracias por hacerme reír, babas 
I needed that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_629
text_en: You got it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_630
text_en: You got it. <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo5_631
text_en: I'll see what I can do.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo5_632
text_en:
Back to work, ¿no? 
We're both too busy for this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_633
text_en: adsvfbghfyjtgukyilo;

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_634
text_en:
¡MIERDA! 
Lo siento, Tláloc ran across the keys He has NO manners

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_635
text_en: LOL! Aww. Hi, Tláloc.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_636
text_en: Who's Tláloc?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_637
text_en: Lol! I have a kavat at home that does that, only last time she sat on the orbiter controls she broke them. ... Kavats weigh a bit more than rats...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_638
text_en:
He is always in the middle of things 
Or nibbling on things he shouldn't be

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_639
text_en:
Mm? 
Oh, one of my rats 
Named after the ancient god of rain

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_640
text_en: You have pets?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_641
text_en: I do! Kavats, kubrows, predasites, vulpaphyla, all types of sub-species.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_642
text_en: They're less pets and more "murder animals" I keep around to help me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_643
text_en:
He's a dick 
The rat, not the god jajaja 
I don't need that kind of bad mojo

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_644
text_en:
Those names mean nothing to me, babas 
But do you care about them?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_645
text_en: How many rats do you have?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_646
text_en: What're your other rats names?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_647
text_en:
4 
Vaquero, Anita, Neenah, and Tláloc

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_648
text_en: Vaquero, Anita, and Neenah

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_649
text_en: Of course I do. They fight beside me, sure, but I love them.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_650
text_en: In the same way I care about the guns I own.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_651
text_en:
Good 
Animals deserve nothing but love and loyalty 
They fight for you because that is what they feel for you 
I am sure my panquecitos would fight for me if they could jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_652
text_en:
Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón 
Abusing and then abandoning those poor Cavia 
Disgusting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_653
text_en:
Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón
Taking the love of that man and using him for his own gain 
Disgusting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_654
text_en:
Just as bad as that Entrati cabrón
 Starting a family only to abandon them when they were of no use 
 Disgusting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_655
text_en: Lárgate de aquí, cabrón

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_656
text_en: If I wanted to be friends with your rats, how would I do that?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_657
text_en: How hard is it to take care of rats?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_658
text_en: I'm trying to picture one of your rats in battle and I'm laughing my ass off.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_659
text_en:
Like all creatures, food is the easiest path to love jaja 
But if you hold them, do not grab them, let them explore and get used to you 
Make clicking noises not kissy noises, kissy noises sound like bad squeaks to them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_660
text_en:
Not very 
They need a big cage with bedding, places to hide, things to do, things to chew on 
They are social and need exercise, so I take them out of their cage a lot to roam

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_661
text_en:
Tláloc has the attitude but not the size for sure jaja 
Maybe we could make them little battle armor 
No, they are too small and fragile 
It would break my heart if anything happened to them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_662
text_en: Can you show me, sometime?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_663
text_en: Sounds complicated.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_664
text_en:
I would love that 
And maybe you can show me some of your strange pets in return

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_665
text_en:
Not much to ask for when you get so much in return from them 
Ni modo, some people do not understand I suppose

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_666
text_en: Me, too. They're too cute.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank3Convo6_667
text_en: I should introduce you to some of my pets sometime.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_668
text_en:
They are 
Esto ha sido divertido, pero... 
Duty calls

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo6_669
text_en:
I would love that 
And maybe then I will introduce you to my rats in return

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_879
text_en: And how are you so sure that this gata mutante is not one of these cavia

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_670
text_en: So, I never got the whole story of how you met Arthur.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_671
text_en: Do you have a second to chat, Lettie? Or are you busy?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_672
text_en: [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_880
text_en: I mean, she's never said anything.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_673
text_en:
Always busy 
But I can take a break 
¿Qué onda?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_674
text_en: I was wondering how you and Arthur met.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_675
text_en:
Eh, it was messy 
Figured you didn't want the gory details 
But, sí, if you want to know 
I'll tell you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_676
text_en:
We were stationed together in the same base 
Him in the Britannic and me with the Libertatian Army 
Different countries, same enemies

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_677
text_en:
I was the field medic for my regiment 
We were deployed in next to his 
The place went real cagadero 
Real fast

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_678
text_en:
Most of my crew didn't make it 
Most of his didn't either 
We held each other together 
Literally 
I stitched his arm up good jaja 
When he retired and went into the ICR 
I followed him without question 
I was sick of all the drama that goes on in the army anyway

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_679
text_en:
I told him I'd follow him to the ends of the earth 
Didn't realize I'd follow him to the edge of Mictlán

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_680
text_en:
It must seem so small to you 
A story like that 
You fight monsters and gods 
You have danced with La Flaca so many times

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_681
text_en: Just because my fights are a bit spectacular doesn't mean I can't appreciate how horrible it must've been.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_682
text_en: All war is shit, end of story.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo1_683
text_en: Eh, little people, little stories.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_684
text_en: Seguro

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_685
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Bright and flashy or small and personal 
La Flaca is all the same in the end 
At least... she should be 
But not for los fantasmas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo1_686
text_en:
Sí, It's all the same 
No matter how big and stupid the guns

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_881
text_en: I guess I don't really know.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_687
text_en:
Tell me of this terrible god you have unleashed 
Your Xipe Totec, your flayed god 
What does he want?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_882
text_en:
So what? 
Smart enough to play dumb 
But she spies on us for him I know it 
We shouldn't trust her

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_688
text_en: Huh? What're you talking about?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_689
text_en: This void creature that sacrifices others and wears their skin like ancient flayed god of old, Xipe Totec

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_690
text_en: What does he want

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_691
text_en: I don't know.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_692
text_en: Freedom?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_693
text_en: Knowledge?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_694
text_en:
You think but you do not know 
Its motivations are not clear 
But yet you think its an enemy ¿Por qué?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_695
text_en: BRB [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_696
text_en:
You treat him like an enemy though 
If you do not know what he is after 
¿Por qué?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_697
text_en: That THING decided it'd be a fun experiment to turn the parents on the Zariman against their children -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_698
text_en: All it does is leave death and destruction in its wake. No matter what it's motivations are, it doesn't matter. Trust me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_699
text_en: And then gave the children magical void powers so they could murder their own parents so it could LEARN from the slaughter.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_700
text_en:
No 
Trust you to understand the mind of a god 
Don't care how old you are 
How much you've seen

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_701
text_en: It's had an opportunity to learn from love, from sacrifice, from kindness. But it  seems to CHOOSE to seek out chaos and murder.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_702
text_en: Even if it's just a toddler smashing toys together to understand the world around it, we're those toys. It has to be stopped.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_703
text_en:
You are not a god babas 
Don't pretend you think like one 
Otherwise you are no better than that Entrati cabrón

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_704
text_en:
You are not a god babas 
Don't pretend you think like one 
Otherwise you are no better than those  orokin cabrones

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_705
text_en:
You are not a god babas 
Don't pretend you think like one

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_706
text_en: I'll continue to hold out hope it isn't an enemy, but... it's not giving me a lot of reasons to think it isn't.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_707
text_en: I refuse to believe it's benign after all I've seen. After all it's done to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_708
text_en: And you think you can stop a god

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_709
text_en: No clue. I tend to make this shit up as I go. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_710
text_en: I think I can try. Like I did here. And that's all any of us can do.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_711
text_en: It's up to others, now. My place is here in 1999 with all of you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo2_712
text_en: I have faith.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_713
text_en:
Jaja, sí 
I get that sense 
Appreciate the honesty, babas 
Seems to work for you, so I won't judge

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_714
text_en:
Sí 
All we can ask for I suppose

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_715
text_en:
Estás bromeando, ¿verdad? 
The moment they ring you will go running 
You are a drifter, a soldier, you will go to save the future when they need you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_716
text_en:
We are trapped here 
Do not lie to me or tell me you'll take me for walks, babas 
Someday you will escape and never come back

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo2_717
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Faith in what does not matter I suppose 
As long as it gets you through

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_883
text_en:
Sí 
She could be a spy 
Working for Entrati 
We shouldn't trust her

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_718
text_en:
Babas... lo siento 
I'm sorry

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_719
text_en: For what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_720
text_en: Yeah, well. You're not exactly making me want to stick around.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_721
text_en: For saying you will leave us here

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_722
text_en:
¡Ash!... ya sé, ya sé 
I...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_724
text_en: What're you afraid of?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_725
text_en: *You're* afraid of something? Holy shit, get Eleanor, we have a newspaper article to write.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_726
text_en:
Los fantasmas we have become 
This eternity of... this 
Of no change, of no death

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_727
text_en:
It TERRIFIES me, babas 
So the fact that you can just LEAVE 
But you say you WON'T?! 
No, imposible

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_728
text_en:
I would run as far and fast as I could from here 
And never ever look back

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_729
text_en: I guess because I've lived through a loop before, I'm not so scared of it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_730
text_en: Yeah, but... I have something valuable keeping me here.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_731
text_en:
Sí, experience will do that 
But you'll get bored in time 
Like Amir with his little games

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_732
text_en:
¿Sí? 
¿Qué es?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_733
text_en: El chamaco is surrounded by those cassettes and keeps saying he has nothing to play

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_734
text_en:
You'll do the same to us 
Toss us aside like a game you're tired of 
Once you've played us enough

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_735
text_en: The Hex.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_736
text_en: Big Bytes Pizza.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_737
text_en: You.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_738
text_en:
Mmhm 
Because we are so special to you 
You would give up freedom 
Esas son pendejadas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_739
text_en:
JAJA 
You had me going 
I needed a laugh

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_740
text_en:
Jajaja, ¿ay, sí? 
Very smooth 
I almost believe you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_741
text_en:
Back to it for both of us 
No rest for los fantasmas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_742
text_en: I'm sure you and I could find ways of keeping things interesting... ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_743
text_en: I can't make promises about the future, Lettie. It hasn't been written yet.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_744
text_en: You can choose to believe me or not.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_745
text_en:
Ay, sí 
I know 
I just came to say I am sorry and explain why, that is all

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_746
text_en:
Jajaja, ay, sí 
Oh, the games we could play 
Very tempting, babas 
Very tempting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_747
text_en:
Back to it for both of us 
No rest for los fantasmas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_884
text_en: Entrati left, and she stayed. I don't think she's still working for him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_748
text_en: For someone who's job is to prevent death, you seem pretty chill with it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_749
text_en: I'd love to know more about how you became a medic.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_750
text_en:
Mm, sí, suppose I am 
Two reasons for that 
Uno, I see La Flaca all the time in my line of work 
She and I are old "friends" 
Dos, my people think about death differently, I think

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_751
text_en:
Jaja how is the easy part, babas 
I enlisted and was bad at it 
Then I got good at it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_752
text_en: Makes sense. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_753
text_en: What do you mean, your people think about death differently?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_754
text_en: Why'd you end up becoming a medic?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_755
text_en: Okay, *why* did you end up becoming a medic?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_756
text_en: Thanks. Good talk. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_757
text_en: The dead people I have experience with are a bit more... intense, yeah.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_758
text_en:
Mi papá was in the army 
We traveled a lot, from base to base 
But when mi tía got sick she moved in with us 
And I learned to take care of her until she passed

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_759
text_en:
We celebrate our beloved ones that return and visit us 
Invite them to come back to see us once a year 
We make our pan de muerto, our calaveritas de azúcar, and set out our marigolds to invite them home

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_760
text_en: That's beautiful.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_761
text_en: Oh... I'm sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_762
text_en: How old were you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_763
text_en:
We sit at their graves and we tell stories 
We eat what we bring for them, with them 
We talk to them and laugh with them 
We do not whisper or cry when they come to us in the night

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_764
text_en:
Eh, está bien 
It happens, ¿no? 
Heart troubles made her sicker and sicker 
Good practice for the future, being a set of hands for mi mamá

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_765
text_en:
10? 11? 
Mi mamá needed the help 
I didn't mind 
Good practice for the future, being a set of hands

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_766
text_en:
I was introduced to La Flaca when I was young 
Mi papá was in the army 
We traveled a lot, from base to base 
But when mi tía got sick she moved in with us 
And I learned to take care of her until she passed

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_767
text_en: Do you miss your aunt?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_768
text_en: I know what it's like to lose family early in life.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_769
text_en: How old were you when you joined the army?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_770
text_en:
No 
I see her once a year at the festival of the dead 
¡Mierda! Before you ask no, it's not like what it sounds 
We do not dig them up we celebrate their souls jajaja 
Well, some do - but we do not, depends on where you're from

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_771
text_en:
Sí, but I do not miss them 
They are gone from my day to day but not gone from my soul they still visit me once a year at the festival of the dead 
We do not dig them up we celebrate their souls jajaja 
Well, some do - but we do not, depends on where you're from

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_772
text_en:
Mi papá made me wait until I was 20 before I joined 
But I was ready to go earlier jajaja 
Biting at the bit, wanted to make him and mi tía proud 
I'm glad he made me wait I wasn't ready

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_773
text_en: Phew. I was going to say. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_774
text_en: LOL! It sounds like a cool holiday, though.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_775
text_en:
We build ofrendas to our loved ones and make pan de muerto, and calaveritas de azúcar, and set out our marigolds to invite them home 
We eat what we bring for them, with them 
We sit at their graves and we tell stories of them 
We talk to them and we laugh with them

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_776
text_en:
Watching your tía slowly die of heart failure is one thing 
Watching people kill each other violently 
Screaming deaths, bleeding deaths 
They are something else

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_777
text_en:
But you know this, don't you? 
You know La Flaca just as well as I do 
Speaking of 
She waits for no one and certainly not for our conversations

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_778
text_en:
Mi tía comes to me every year, pats me on the shoulder and says "Buen trabajo, amorcito, sigue así" 
And it makes me smile not scream and run away in fear

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_779
text_en:
I hope she comes out this far... 
I'll have to make her paper marigolds 
Maybe Arthur will help me make some pan de muerto I am a shit baker jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_780
text_en: I'm sure he'd love to help.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_781
text_en: I'd love to help, too.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_782
text_en:
You are sweet 
Sí, maybe we can work together

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_783
text_en:
If you want, we could build an ofrenda to your family 
Maybe they would come to see their babas after so long 
I am sure they are so proud of you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_784
text_en:
Do you have loved ones you want to have visit 
We could work together and build you an ofrenda 
Maybe they would come to see their babas after so long I am sure they are so proud of you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_785
text_en: I... would love that, actually. Thank you, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_786
text_en: I'd love to help you, but let's leave my family in the future where they belong.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_787
text_en: Um... I don't think they'd want to see me...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_788
text_en:
Claro, friend 
Mm, now that I think 
Can souls travel through time? 
Ay, equis, is the thought that counts sometimes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_789
text_en:
Fair 
Mm, now that I think 
Can souls travel through time? 
Ay, equis, is the thought that counts sometimes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_790
text_en:
Because of what your Xipe Totec made you do 
It was not your fault, they were driven mad 
Sometimes you need to cauterize the wound 
You put them down, it was not murder

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_791
text_en: ¿Por qué?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_885
text_en: Do you really think she's spying on us for him? Why?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_792
text_en: That's not how it felt.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_793
text_en: You're right...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_794
text_en: Because when the Man in the Wall drove the parents insane, they attacked the children, and... the children with void powers had to kill them, and....

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo3_795
text_en: I can't talk about this. I'm sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_796
text_en:
Sí, I can't imagine how it felt 
To have to hurt your own family like that 
But you had no choice, solecito 
They were rabid animals and had no control

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_797
text_en:
And that kind of choice I *do* understand 
But that is a story for another time 
La Flaca waits for no one and not our conversations and I have a line

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_798
text_en:
You had no choice, solecito 
They were rabid animals and had no control 
And that kind of choice I *do* understand

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_799
text_en:
Your Xipe Totec did this, your flayed god 
It was his actions that drove them mad and got them killed

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_800
text_en:
Ay, sí 
I understand

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo3_801
text_en:
But that is a story for another time 
La Flaca waits for no one and not our conversations and I have a line

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_886
text_en:
No, see 
It's exactly that reason why I think she is 
He's gone and needs eyes here on us, ¿no? 
Don't know why, pero no me gusta

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_802
text_en: Hypothetical question: If I wanted to ask you out for drinks, would I end up with stitches?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_803
text_en:
Sí 
You would

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_804
text_en:
Mm? 
Jajaja, no

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_805
text_en:
But I don't drink, never have 
Don't do drugs, either 
You'll have to be more creative to get into my pants 
Or whatever it is I have to wear now

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_806
text_en: Good to know. :) Any hints on what I can do to win you over, then?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_807
text_en: On that topic, do you... I've been meaning to ask...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo6_887
text_en:
¡No sé! 
Not my job to predict a crazy pendejo 
Keeping tabs on us maybe 
I don't like it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_808
text_en:
You just should be real certain that you know what you're for, babas 
If you like it sweet and gentle go talk to Aoi or Amir 
I am too used to pain and like it too much for that kind of thing

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_809
text_en: ¿Qué?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_810
text_en: I've been curious if you and the other protoframes still had... y'know... your... y'know... parts...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_811
text_en: Uh - Never mind.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_812
text_en:
JAJAJAJAJA 
Are you serious?! 
You can't just ASK people what they - 
Aaaay babaaaaassss I have not laughed so hard in a looooong time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_813
text_en:
Va 
Busy anyway

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_814
text_en: Sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_815
text_en: Um... well? Do you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_816
text_en:
I tell you what 
Maybe if you are a good little babas 
You just might find out, mm? 
Just warning you 
If you like it sweet and gentle go talk to Aoi or Amir 
I am too used to pain and like it too much for that kind of thing

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_817
text_en: Yes ma'am. Consider me warned.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo4_818
text_en: Um... Yeah, never mind. Pain's not really my thing.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_819
text_en:
Bueno 
You're better off that way 
You can let me know if you change your mind

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_820
text_en:
Mm, yeah? 
Think you can take it, do you? 
We'll see

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_821
text_en:
Now vete 
Can't be daydreaming when I've got work to do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo4_822
text_en:
Now vete 
I've got work to do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_823
text_en:
Ay, friend 
You got a second?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_824
text_en: You're usually the super busy one. :)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_825
text_en: Yeah, what's up?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_826
text_en: Sorry, just about to go. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_827
text_en:
Ay, sí, jajaja I usually am 
Just had a question 
Someone like you 
Do you ever feel homesick?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_828
text_en:
Just had a question 
Someone like you 
Do you ever feel homesick?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_829
text_en: I've never had a real home, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_830
text_en: What do you mean, "someone like me?"

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_831
text_en: The only places I've ever had to call "home" have tried to KILL me. Why would I miss them?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_832
text_en:
Sí, I know 
I'm the same

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_833
text_en: Someone with no real home

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_834
text_en:
Because you can want something you never had 
Or miss things you see other people having 
I know I do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo6_888
text_en: Either way, she's smart enough to understand "If you mess with Lettie's rats, you sleep outside." Is that good enough?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_835
text_en: Way to rub it in, Lettie. Thanks.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_836
text_en: Can't miss what you've never had.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_837
text_en:
No 
That's a lie 
I grew up without a home and I get homesick

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_838
text_en:
Nonono 
I don't mean it like that 
I'm the same

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_839
text_en:
Details are different but you and me 
Neither of us had a real home 
Bouncing from place to place, base to base 
Never settling, never making friends for long 
Never knowing where I'd be in six months, a year, two

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_840
text_en:
All I had were my family and their traditions 
But sometimes I think they didn't even belong to me 
Like you and those pinches orokin

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_841
text_en: At least you had your family, though. I didn't even have that.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_842
text_en: At least you weren't alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_843
text_en:
Sí 
You're right 
How you aren't licking the wallpaper jaja 
I have no idea I would have lost my mind

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_844
text_en:
Maybe I still will 
Trapped here como un fantasma 
Ay, equis, I'm babbling

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_845
text_en: How so?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_846
text_en: You seem really proud of your background, I'm surprised.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_847
text_en:
Sí 
I am because I learned no one can take it from me 
But it took me a long time to get there

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_848
text_en:
Being called slurs because of my skin or how I talk by everybody 
Too gringa to be Tenochtitlán 
Too Tenochtitlán to be gringa 
Ay, equis, I'm babbling

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_849
text_en:
I miss a place and a thing I never had 
I wonder if it's genetics 
Something raised in us 
Makes no sense

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_850
text_en:
That's why I was asking 
See if you had it too 
But you're from the future 
Maybe they fixed it by then

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_851
text_en: No, I think I know how you feel. I... get these bouts of sadness where I get an urge to go somewhere that doesn't exist.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo5_852
text_en: Maybe. I really don't get homesick. I get sad and lonely sometimes, but it isn't homesickness.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_853
text_en:
Sí 
That's what I mean 
Or maybe we both have the same kind of depression jajaja 
Stupid spiders

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_854
text_en:
Sí 
Maybe just my depression rearing its head again 
Wouldn't be surprised 
Stupid spiders

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo5_855
text_en:
Ehn, gracias 
Speaking of spiders, time to put them and me to sleep

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1664
text_en: I don't feel that strongly, I'm sorry...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1665
text_en: I - I love you too, Lettie. I never believed... I'm just so happy.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1666
text_en:
Ay 
Sí 
Ok

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1667
text_en:
JAJAJA síí 
I am hard to read I know 
Aggh I am so happy too 
Lets celebrate tonight, ¿mm?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1668
text_en: This... is why I do not trust people jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1669
text_en:
I don't want you asking 
I don't want you being NICE 
I want you to show me what you WANT, ¿entendiste?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1670
text_en: Yes. Ma'am.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1671
text_en: <RETRO_EMOJI_SNEAKY>

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1672
text_en:
That's the spirit 
Here's to us, mi corazón 
And here is to the future 
Filled with fantasmas and endless futures and gods and demons as they may be 
We have our love 
And that is more than enough

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank3Convo4_893
text_en:
Sí 
The stale popcorn and greasy pizza 
Ay, equis, you do you, I won't stop you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1673
text_en:
Is okay it happens 
Stupid me making mistakes again 
Better for me we don't go on like this then 
You understand

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieBirthdayConvo_894
text_en:
What is star days?
Whatever. Too busy for that shit.
Adiós

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieBirthdayConvo_895
text_en:
Jajaja no
All I want is to sleep in an hour or a fresh cup of coffee. That too much to ask? 
Pero, gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_896
text_en: So how'd you end up getting involved in the whole Arthur/Hex thing?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_897
text_en:
Mm 
Not a fun story, friend 
Worse than the bloodbath where Arthur and I became hermanos 
Not fun to hear 
Mierda, not fun to tell

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_898
text_en:
Somos hermanos, Arthur and I 
We go way back 
I promised to follow him anywhere 
Seems like he meant to the edge of Mictlán

text_en: You seem to really... REALLY hate Entrati. Why?

text_en:
Sí 
Maybe I do 
But after everything you told me 
About how he mistreated those poor animals 
Abandoned his family 
And that man who loves him 
How could I not hate that cabrón?!

text_en:

text_en: If you're not comfortable telling me, that's fine.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_909
text_en: No problem. Plenty of shit I haven't told you, yet.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_910
text_en:
Not about comfort, babas 
You want to hear about all the times I've had to put someone down or take off a limb 
The times I've had a mother weeping next to their dead child and had to tell her I couldn't save her 
I see it all the time 
Me vale madre

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_911
text_en:
Sí 
We all have the things we don't tell people 
Until we're very certain we can trust them not to change how they feel

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_912
text_en:
We were stationed together in the same base 
Him in the Britannic and me with the Libertatian Army 
Different countries, same enemies

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_913
text_en:
I was the field medic for my regiment
We were deployed in next to his
The place went real cagadero
Real fast

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_914
text_en:
Most of my crew didn't make it 
Most of his didn't either 
We held each other together 
Literally 
I stitched his arm up good jaja 
When he retired and went into the ICR 
I followed him without question 
I was sick of all the drama that goes on in the army anyway

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_915
text_en: Okay? I'm sorry?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_916
text_en: Then what's the problem?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_917
text_en: Sí, como quieras

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_918
text_en:
It might change how you look at some of us babas 
And I don't know if I trust you enough not to walk away

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_919
text_en: The way you talk about him, and because I know how much trust is important to you... It seems personal.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_920
text_en: I know how much you hate it when people break the trust of others. Especially animals.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_921
text_en: People who hurt animals have a special place in hell, absolutely. But it seems like there's more going on than that.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_922
text_en: Yeah, but it seems like a personal grudge you have against him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_923
text_en: The way you talk about him, and because I know how much trust is important to you... It seems personal.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_924
text_en: Yeah, but it seems like a personal grudge you have against him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_925
text_en: Good enough for me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_926
text_en:
Sí 
Ese cabrón se puede ir brincando a la chingada

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_927
text_en:
Ay, sí
You caught on
Need a new nickname for you, ¿eh babas? Jaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_928
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Animals most of all deserve the best we can give them 
And when trust is broken like that 
It makes me want to kill a man 
Specifically THAT one

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_929
text_en:
Sí, I do 
I have my reasons

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_930

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_931

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_932
text_en: If you're not comfortable telling me, that's fine.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_934

Not fun to hear 
Mierda, not fun to tell

Not fun to hear

text_en:

Not something I want to get into
Not today

text_en: Why not?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_941
text_en: I get it. Not a problem.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_942

Not today

No dejes que se te suba a la cabeza

You know how to make me smile 
But it doesn't mean they should be allowed to spread their diseases

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_979

¿Ay, sí?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_982

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_983
text_en: What do you mean, "spread their diseases?"

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_984

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_985

Jajaja

Ay, equis

Pero it's not a story I'm telling today

Back to work for both of us

Mmm why are you asking, ¿babas?
Has no one told you what happened?

text_en: How'd you wind up meeting Entrati, though?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_999
text_en: Can I ask what happened next?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_1000
text_en:
Sí, you just did jajaja
But I get what you're asking
And you've been dancing around the subject like you want to do the tango
You know I don't want to talk about it
Has no one told you what happened?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_1001
text_en: I'm just trying to get the whole picture.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_1002
text_en: No one else will tell me. They just avoid the subject.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo7_1003

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo7_1004
text_en:
Ay, sííí
I'm sure you are
And if nobody else will tell you I guess it's up to Mamá Lettie
Well this story is one I don't like to tell
Especially because I've gotten used to having you underfoot

Mmm and you wonder why 
And figure Mamá Lettie would tell you the truth 
Normally you'd be right, babas 
But this one I don't like to tell 
Especially because I've gotten used to having you underfoot

JAJAJA Sííí

This one I don't like to tell

Oh and babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1008
text_en: So... Lettie, look... I know you already said "no" to Amir's game, but...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1009
text_en: Hey, Lettie, we're friends, now, yeah? You like me now, ish?
