text_en: Hey Lettie, what do you think about tabletop roleplaying games?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1011
text_en: Hey Lettie, I have a favor to ask you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1012
text_en:
Aayyyy 
¿Otra vez, babas?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1013
text_en:
¿A poco sí?
más o menos jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1014
text_en:
Estás bromeando, ¿verdad? 
Amir is making you ask I know it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1015
text_en:
¿Ay, sí? 
What is it babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1016
text_en: I agreed to ask, I think it'll be fun!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1017
text_en: I agreed to ask, it's important to him.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1018
text_en:
Babas... 
I have too much shit to do 
Than to waste it on games for children

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1019
text_en: Amir's putting together a game of Fables & Frontiers. And I know it sounds silly, but before you come over here and stab me -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1020
text_en: It's a chance to get everybody to spend time together.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1021
text_en: It's really important to Amir

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1022
text_en: I know a game like "Fables & Frontiers" sounds really silly, but it's about spending time together.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1023
text_en: I know a game like "Fables & Frontiers" sounds really silly, but it's important to Amir.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1024
text_en: And you could use a break.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1025
text_en: And it might actually be a little fun.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1026
text_en: ...And you wouldn't be the only one playing with us?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1027
text_en:
¿Sí? 
Who else have you talked into this?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1028
text_en: ...And you DO kind of owe me a favor, don't you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1029
text_en: So what do you think?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1030
text_en:
Babas... 
Lo siento, I just have so much shit to do 
You'll have to go on without me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1031
text_en: Me and Amir, obviously. And after that...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1032
text_en: Eleanor said yes, not sure if that's helping or hurting my case...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1033
text_en: Aoi said she'd play

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1034
text_en: Quincy's in

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank4Convo8_1035
text_en: Arthur said he'd play lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1036
text_en: Of course the bruja wants to waste time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1037
text_en: I am not surprised...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1038
text_en:
¡¿Neta?! 
QUINCY 
How much did you pay him

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1039
text_en: HAH... well, if mi hermano is playing...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1040
text_en:
Ssíííííí... 
Fiiine, babaaass... 
But I better not regret this...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1045
text_en: You holding up?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1046
text_en: How're you doing today, sweetheart?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1047
text_en: How's my favorite badass doing today?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1048
text_en: Hey Lettie, can I ask you something about your rats?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1049
text_en: Hey Lettie, what's your favorite kind of food?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1050
text_en:
No 
I am not holding up 
I have not been okay for a long time 
But I have to be the one to pretend 
Always have to be the strong one, don't I?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1051
text_en: Like shit

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1052
text_en: Not now babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1053
text_en:
But what if I don't want to be 
What if I'm not 
What if I feel myself falling apart and-- 
Lo siento, solecito, you did not ping me for this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1054
text_en: Is everything okay?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1055
text_en: I - um - yikes. Should I message you later?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1056
text_en: If you're busy, we can chat later.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1057
text_en: Sorry?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1058
text_en:
NO 
Everything is not okay 
Nothing has been okay for a long time 
But time has no meaning anymore does it?! 
You and that cabrón saw to that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1059
text_en:
Vete 
There will be no later

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1060
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Your sorries could cover the walls 
Then maybe they'd be good for something

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1061
text_en: Yeah, I just... wanted to see if you wanted to go get some coffee.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1062
text_en: I'm here for you, Lettie. And I care. Talk to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1063
text_en:
Sí 
Sounds good

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1064
text_en:
You aren't my therapist 
You don't need to hear me whining like some silly little niña

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1065
text_en: Did I do something to piss you off?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1066
text_en: Is something wrong?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1067
text_en:
SÍ 
Everything has been wrong for a long time 
But time has no meaning anymore does it?! 
You and that cabrón saw to that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1068
text_en: How is any of this my fault?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1069
text_en: Um... I'm getting the feeling you're looking for a fight.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1070
text_en:
Maybe I am 
Maybe I'm not 
Maybe I've finally had it with all this pendejadas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1071
text_en:
You and your pinche time loop bullshit 
If it weren't for that we'd be dead

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1072
text_en: Lettie, you and I are supposed to be in a relationship. And that *means* something to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1073
text_en: Lettie, you and I have become close friends. I care about you. And that *means* something to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1074
text_en: I think you're one of the strongest people I've ever met in my *life.* You're not capable of whining.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1674
text_en: So if you want to talk? I'm here.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1675
text_en: Talk to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1075
text_en: Wait. Back up. Are you PISSED that you aren't dead?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1076
text_en: I'm not your punching bag, Lettie. And I don't need this.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1077
text_en: I need you to back up and tell me what's wrong.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1078
text_en:
Sí 
Run scared, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1079
text_en:
I'M PISSED THAT I CAN'T DIE, BABAS 
Don't you understand 
How little life matters without death 
I find myself asking why 
WHY BOTHER?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1080
text_en:
Nnnh solecito I hate compliments 
Fine, fine... I just find myself standing here looking at the line of civvies and wondering 
Why bother you know?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1081
text_en:
Nnnh, buddy, I hate compliments 
Fine, fine... I just find myself standing here looking at the line of civvies and wondering 
Why bother you know?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1082
text_en:
They get shot or killed 
I patch them up or I don't and they die 
They don't understand it doesn't matter 
That if they die, on the new year 
They'll be right back at the start

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1083
text_en:
What's the point?! 
What's the point in any of this babas 
We are all fantasmas playing out our old lives and old deaths 
Walking through dreams that will never change 
WHY?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1084
text_en:
I stand here 
Patching civvies back together 
Day in day out 
They don't understand it doesn't matter 
That if they die here, right now, they'll just COME BACK 
That they are just sleepwalking fantasmas 
While we know what we suffer through

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1085
text_en:
They are just fantasmas sleepwalking through a nightmare 
We are los fantasmas who know what we are 
Don't know which is worse

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1086
text_en:
I could go on a rampage 
Murder them all in cold blood 
And come the new year 
They'd all be back, ¿no?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1087
text_en: Yeah? But... please don't, though. It'd be really hard to explain to the others.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1088
text_en: But things here CAN still change. Maybe not much, but in ways that matter. Look around.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1089
text_en:
What if I took a toaster in the bath 
Killed myself 
What then?! 
I know I died in that other memory 
That nightmare

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1090
text_en:
Ay, sí 
We collect strays now, bueno, a few fantasmas suffer a little less 
A few things change here and there, sure 
But what about what you made us 
I know I died in that other memory

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1091
text_en:
You should have left me there 
Let me die 
We do not belong as fantasmas 
We are antinaturales, people should not live forever, they should be allowed to die

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1092
text_en: But you know what you have here that can help you through it? A family. If you choose to let yourself have one.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1093
text_en: But things here CAN still change. Maybe not much, but in ways that matter. Look around.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1094
text_en: We've given these people a new home. A new sense of hope. Maybe just a few, and maybe it doesn't matter in the end...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1095
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I just get so tired of the fight, you know? 
I forget I'm not in this battle alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1096
text_en: But isn't that why you're a healer? Isn't the act of trying, of that sense of hope, that kindness, what matters, and not where we wind up in the end?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1097
text_en: I know you never felt like you've had somewhere to belong. You've never had a home before, Lettie. Like me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1098
text_en: Look around. At the civvies. At the Hex. At me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1099
text_en: This could be your family. Your home. If you wanted it to be. If you LET it be.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1100
text_en: This could be your family. If you wanted it to be. If you LET it be.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1101
text_en: I... know how you feel, Lettie. I do. All my life, I've been the victim of somebody else's plans. The Orokin. The Man in the Wall. Now Entrati.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1102
text_en: You have a choice, Lettie. You can either spend eternity feeling like a victim or you can see this as a chance for what it is - a new kind of life.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1103
text_en: But I had a choice, when I watched you all die. I could let you all stay victims, too... or I could try to save you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1104
text_en: Yes, it's a time loop. Yes, not much changes. But you know what DOES change that matters? Us. Who WE are. What WE know. And what WE feel.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1105
text_en:
Life is about the moments we have 
The moments we spend caring for each other 
And now... we have an eternity of those, don't we? 
Gracias, solecito ... neta

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1106
text_en: So maybe it wasn't my choice to make for you. And if you want to hate me for that? Fine. Hate me for that.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1107
text_en: So no, this isn't the kind of life you're used to. You won't get to experience "normal" ever again.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1108
text_en: And it just hurts me to see you like this when I care about you like family.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1109
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I just get so tired of the fight, you know? 
I forget I'm not in this battle alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1110
text_en: And it just hurts me to see you like this when I care about you like family.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1111
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I get stuck in my own head and I forget I'm not alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1663
text_en:
Here's to us, my friend 
And here is to the future 
Filled with fantasmas and endless futures and gods and demons as they may be 
We have each other 
And that is plenty good enough

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1114
text_en: But you never would have let the team die if you could have saved them. Because you wouldn't let them stay the victims.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1115
text_en: But there are things here that can make it a life worth living.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1116
text_en: And... there's another reason it hurts me to see you like this. [Confess feelings.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1117
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I get stuck in my own head and I forget I'm not alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1118
text_en:
I need to remember that I have a familia here around me 
People I can rely on when things get dark 
Gracias, solecito ... en serio

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1119
text_en:
Life is about the moments we have 
The moments we spend caring for each other 
And now... we have an eternity of those, don't we? 
Gracias ... en serio

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1120
text_en:
I need to remember that I have a familia here around me 
People I can rely on when things get dark 
Gracias... en serio

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1121
text_en:
Victims saved for what reason 
This is no life babas 
This nightmare of fantasmas is no life at all

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1122
text_en:
Ay sí 
Stale pizza and an abandoned mall 
Sad stray civilians 
And a never ending war against scaldra 
Tell me why is this LIFE worth living

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1123
text_en: ¿Ay sí?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1124
text_en: Do you think this is just a casual fling for me?! Do you think you really mean that little to me?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1125
text_en: Look around. Look at what YOU have. At the family around you. At the people that care about YOU.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1126
text_en: You see strays, I see people showing each other kindness in the darkest times. And I think that's beautiful.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1127
text_en: Are you really so oblivious that you can't tell how much you mean to me?! [Confess feelings.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1128
text_en: Yeah, okay, sure. That's definitely what's going on here. You're right. I'm just being naïve and my feelings aren't real.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1129
text_en:
You tell me, is it? 
Do I? 
I see someone who has spent their whole lives alone and has a chance at something they never had 
Maybe doesn't understand what they've gotten themselves into

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1130
text_en: And I see someone who's hurting and trying to pick a fight instead of processing that pain.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1131
text_en: I know you feel like you lost your life. Your family.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1132
text_en:
Sí 
Glad you agree 
Now vete

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1133
text_en: And if you want to exclude yourself from that, so be it. But that's YOUR choice, Lettie. You're making that decision, no one else.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1134
text_en: Before you tell me I'm stupid, or whatever - or that I can't handle you, just wait, and let me talk.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1135
text_en:
¡¿Ay, sí?! 
Do tell

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1136
text_en: Nobody thought the Cavia were worth saving, either. Should Loid have just left them to die?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1137
text_en: I also know you never felt like you've had somewhere to belong. You've never had a home before, Lettie. Like me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1138
text_en: This situation you're all in - I won't lie, it sucks. Trust me, I've been there. But you have one thing I don't have.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1139
text_en: Besides, even if it's pointless in the end, stray animals are the ones most worth rescuing, aren't they?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1140
text_en: Isn't the act of caring, the act of TRYING, the whole point?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1141
text_en: We're not done with this conversation, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1142
text_en: I'm done with this. And I'm done with you. [Break up.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1143
text_en:
Sí 
I figured this would happen 
Vete, babas, don't have time for you anymore 
Should have known better than to play with niñitos

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1144
text_en: You're lashing out at me because you're scared. Because you don't want to be trapped here like this. But you're pushing everybody away who can help you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1145
text_en: Mierda

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1146
text_en: So you can either let me in - for real - and help you, or you can push me away, too. That's your decision to make.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1147
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
I get in my own head and I... haven't been giving you a fair shot

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1148
text_en:
It's too easy for me to brush this off as just physical 
Makes it safer, you know? 
Lo siento, solecito...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1149
text_en:
I want to make this up to you 
 Think I know how, too... 
 If you'll let me, mm?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1150
text_en: Maybe later. I'm a little pissed right now.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1151
text_en: Like I'm going to say no to that. :}

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1152
text_en:
Sí 
I get it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1153
text_en: Would that death have been better than life as they are now? Tagfer certainly might have agreed with you once - he lost his wife during the ordeal.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1154
text_en: Well? This could be your family. Your home. If you wanted it to be. If you LET it be.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1155
text_en: You have each other. You have a *family.* You have *friends.*

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1156
text_en: But they found in themselves a new family. A reason to continue on. A reason to keep living.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1157
text_en: You aren't alone like I was - and that loneliness sent me into a spiral of misery and numbness.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1158
text_en: You need to choose which way you want to be. If you want to be alone or not.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1159
text_en: Mierda

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1160
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I get stuck in my own head and I forget I'm not alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1161
text_en:
I need to remember that I have a familia here around me 
People I can rely on when things get dark 
Gracias... en serio

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1162
text_en: It's those moments of kindness that matter, isn't it? Those flashes where we can show people the better parts of ourselves.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1163
text_en: Mierda

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1164
text_en:
Life is about the moments we have 
The moments we spend caring for each other 
Not the ultimate end point 
Gracias... en serio

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1165
text_en:
I... 
I don't think I like it when you call me out on my mentiras 
Sí... you... you're right 
Sometimes I just get so tired of the fight, you know? 
I forget I'm not in this battle alone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1166
text_en: You're drop-dead gorgeous. You're fiercely intelligent. And you could kick my ass. But that's not the only reasons you've become so important to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1167
text_en: Deep down beneath all the layers of armor you've built over yourself, is one of the kindest, most compassionate people I've ever met. But that's not all.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1168
text_en: You're unstoppable. Unbreakable. Unflinching. Nothing seems to slow you down. You're one of the toughest people I've ever met. And -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1169
text_en: Let's stop to consider how damn gorgeous you are, and how you could absolutely break me like a twig if you wanted to. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1170
text_en: You're one of the kindest, most caring people I've ever met. The way you tend to your animals and the way you'll go out of your way for people makes my heart melt.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1171
text_en: You're made of iron. And I know that no matter what they throw at you - Entrati, the Man in the Wall, Viktor and the Scaldra - it doesn't matter. They don't stand a chance.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1172
text_en: Point is... I care about you, Lettie. A lot. And more than just as friend, and I understand if it isn't mutual, but -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1173
text_en: Shut up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1174
text_en: I can't stand to see you give up hope like this. You're not a ghost. You're not a fantasma.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1175
text_en: You're LETTIE, and -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1176
text_en: Aguántame tantito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1177
text_en: I'm sorry if I upset you...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo1_1178
text_en: I understand if you don't feel the same way, I get it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1179
text_en:
¡Neta, ya cállate! 
I need a second to think 
To breathe 
Can't process when I'm tearing up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo1_1180
text_en:
I don't DO compliments, solecito 
Never take them well 
Talk tomorrow, sort this shit out then 
Lo siento

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1181
text_en:
Solecito 
You there

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1182
text_en: Yeah..?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1183
text_en: [Ignore.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1184
text_en:
I... 
Wanted to say 
Primero, lo siento 
I shouldn't have reacted the way I did 
Segundo, do you mean what you said?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1185
text_en: I meant every word.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1186
text_en: I was making that all up.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1187
text_en:
Mm 
Should've known 
Go play with Quincy 
Un escuincle like that seem more your type

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1188
text_en:
Aayyyy... ok... 
Mierda

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1189
text_en: I still don't know if "mierda" is a good thing or not...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1190
text_en: If it's not mutual you can just tell me, I can take it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1191
text_en:
Jajaja it means "shit" 
But nono, this isn't a bad conversation 
It's just--

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1192
text_en:
Look 
Trust is something that is very hard for me to give away 
And it is the most important thing in a relationship for me 
Broken trust is something that cannot be  repaired, especially in a situation like this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1193
text_en:
You know how hard it is for me to trust people 
And how important trust is for me ¿no? 
Well... it's even more important when I get into a relationship with someone

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1194
text_en:
You know trust is something that is very hard for me to give 
And it is the most important thing in a relationship for me 
Broken trust is something that cannot be repaired, especially in a situation like this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1195
text_en:
Because the kind of relationships I like to have tend to hurt, solecito 
If you get what I'm saying 
Only as much as we want it to 
And only as far as you're willing to go 
Because this kind of thing takes trust

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1196
text_en: I'm not saying no, but can I ask...why pain is your thing?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1197
text_en:
And broken trust in a thing like this 
Can not be repaired 
¿Me explico?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1198
text_en: Only if we get to take turns now and then...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1199
text_en:
Mmm, don't know 
Maybe because it's pain that I can control 
Versus all the pain I can't

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1200
text_en: I'm not really into mixing pain and pleasure, sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1201
text_en:
Jajaja of course 
But once you've earned it 
Need to know I can trust you first 
So... what do you say?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1202
text_en:
Or maybe because it's something intense 
Something sharp that cuts through all the rest of the bullshit I have to deal with day in and day out 
It's REAL 
I can sink my teeth into it 
Make it sing 
Feel it pulse

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1205
text_en:
And it DEMANDS trust 
It doesn't work without it, solecito 
So... what do you say?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1206
text_en: Want to make a terrible mistake with me?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1207
text_en: Yeah. I do, actually. :) [Date Lettie.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1203
text_en:
Ay, sí 
Is not for everyone 
Entiendo, no harm no foul

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1208
text_en:
All right 
Brace yourself, solecito 
I won't go easy on you 
Because I've seen you fight 
I know you can take it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieConfession_1209
text_en: I need to think this over, actually. Sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1204
text_en: Let me know if you change your mind

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieConfession_1210
text_en:
But don't worry 
I'll always kiss it better after 
You can count on that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieAmirHack_1211
text_en: VOY A MATAR A ESE PINCHE MOCOSO

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieAmirHack_1212
text_en: I get the feeling you're mad...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieAmirHack_1213
text_en: Um... did you not get the peanut butter...?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieAmirHack_1214
text_en:
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO 
WITH 500 CASES OF KETCHUP PACKETS 
¡DILE A ESE NIÑO QUE VENGA AQUÍ AHORA MISMO! 
GET HIM TO DEAL WITH IT 
NOW!!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieAmirHack_1215
text_en: Hey, so, it was all a mistake. Amir was trying to send you peanut butter for your rats.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieAmirHack_1216
text_en: This is all a misunderstanding. He was trying to send you a gift.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieAmirHack_1217
text_en: But it all got screwed up, and I'll help him deal with it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieAmirHack_1218
text_en:
I DON'T CARE 
¡¡SÁCALAS DE AQUÍ!! 
¡¡AHORA!!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieAmirHack_1219
text_en:
¿SÍ? 
It was for mis panquecitos?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieAmirHack_1220
text_en:
¡Ay equis! 
Just get it all out of here 
¡¡AHORA!!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1221
text_en:
Solecito 
You there? 
I have a few minutes to spare and I wanted to talk

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1222
text_en:
Hey
You there? 
I have a few minutes to spare and I wanted to talk

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1223
text_en: You're not breaking up with me, are you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1224
text_en: YOU want to talk...? Are you feeling okay? Did somebody die?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1225
text_en: I'm sorry, I can't chat right now. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1226
text_en:
¡Ay, no! 
Nonono 
Not what this is about jajaja 
Though YOU might change YOUR mind when I'm done talking

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1227
text_en:
Jaja very funny 
And who hasn't died once at this point 
Ay, no, what I wanted to talk about 
Is serious 
And something I've been avoiding

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1228
text_en: Okay... What's this about?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1229
text_en: All right. I'm listening.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1230
text_en:
You asked how we became these monstruos 
What that pinche cabrón did to us 
Why I hate him so much 
What that piece of shit made us do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1231
text_en:
You should know what that pinche cabrón did to us 
Why I hate him so much 
What that piece of shit made us do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1232
text_en:
I told you how Arthur and I became hermanos 
But not how we got turned into these monstruos 
You should know what that pinche cabrón did to us 
Why I hate him so much 
What that piece of shit made us do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1233
text_en:
You've done a lot for us 
Saved our lives, stayed with us... when you could leave 
Time you hear the whole story

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1234
text_en:
So 
I followed Arthur into the ICR 
Got sent here to this cuchitril to deal with some weird plague nobody'd seen before

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1235
text_en:
A disease that chews up people 
Spits them out half person half machine 
Or some things that weren't ever human beings at all, más bien computadoras

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1236
text_en:
We get deployed to "deal with it" 
Best way we know how 
Half bandages 
Half bullets

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1237
text_en:
This was early 1998 
Before you came 
That Entrati cabrón was already here 
Selling his MENTIRAS

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1238
text_en:
But the best lies are the ones you want to believe, ¿verdad? 
We had no cure for this disease except a dance with La Flaca 
But here he comes 
Doktor F and his magical bag of miracles will cure what ails you 
Saying he can fix it all with his medicina milagrosa

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1239
text_en:
And we bought it como una bola de mensos 
And when the ICR stomps its feet and says "nonono, you cannot help him distribute his drug" should have listened 
Vaccines come from scientists not an old man in some ugly-ass trench coat 
Selling lies like some old world snake oil 
But people are dying all around you? 
You help him anyway because you signed up to HELP people

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1240
text_en:
So we helped him inject the people of this city with his drug 
Lined them up in our tents and that cabrón and I shot them full of it one after another 
And the others kept the operation safe while we worked

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1241
text_en:
NOSOTROS CREÍMOS EN ÉL 
We trusted him 
¿Y por tan poco? 
It seemed like it was working 
The people we were shooting up weren't getting sick 
The problem...?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1242
text_en:
Everybody around them WAS 
Do you know what "silent carriers" are? 
Volunteered in an animal shelter one summer cuando estaba chiquita 
Had all these raccoons 
Couldn't release them, because they might be silent carriers of rabies 
THEY looked healthy, seemed healthy, seemed normal...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1243
text_en:
But if we let them go? 
They'd infect everything they came across... 
That's what we were doing to people 
THAT'S WHAT HE WAS MAKING US DO TO PEOPLE 
¡LO HIZO A PROPÓSITO!
This place is the edge of Mictlán POR SU CULPA

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1244
text_en:
Even when we started to suspect 
We could not believe 
We whispered to each other 
But shook our heads and said 
Nonono, it cannot be 
Not him 
Not us

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1245
text_en:
We did not want to believe 
That our trust had been broken 
We... we had taken the drug too, solecito... 
We were spreading the plague...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1246
text_en:
We did not want to believe 
That our trust had been broken 
We... we had taken the drug too... 
We were spreading the plague...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1247
text_en: So when he said the Techrot strain had mutated... and we were no longer safe...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1248
text_en:
We lined right up 
Like good little soldaditos

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1249
text_en:
Lua, it hurt 
Wasn't the fun kind, either... 
Aoi's screams were the worst 
I could not help her, I was too busy dying too 
She wept in fear and all I wanted to do was hold her

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1250
text_en:
Tell her it would be okay 
That the pain would pass and La Flaca would take her home 
She was so afraid and I could not help her 
My legs would not work...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1251
text_en:
And I will hate that piece of shit 
Every day of my endless life 
For that betrayal

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1252
text_en:
And if I ever see him again? 
You better be there to hold me back 
Or I will teach him what real hurt is like

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1253
text_en: Holding a grudge like that isn't healthy, even if what he did to you was wrong.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1254
text_en: Holy shit... I didn't realize. I - I'm so sorry he used you like that. Yeah... I'd hate him, too.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1255
text_en: I - so - wait. You all are partially to blame for the Techrot spreading?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1256
text_en: Sorry I fell asleep there for a second. What were you saying?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1257
text_en:
Look at you 
All Hail San Babas 
Forgiving sins 
No 
Some things cannot be forgiven 
What he did to us is one of them 
What we did to the people of this city is another

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1258
text_en:
Sí 
I do not take betrayal well 
But we wanted to believe him and it made us stupid 
If you do not want to be around us anymore, I understand
The others will, too

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1259
text_en:
Sí 
We were 
But we wanted to believe him and it made us stupid 
If you do not want to be around us anymore, I understand 
The others will, too

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1260
text_en: I'm not here to tell you what you did can be forgiven or not. That's not something I can do, and honestly - I don't think what you're describing is something that CAN be forgiven.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1261
text_en: Entrati came here and found exactly what he was looking for - useful, skilled people he could trick into doing what he wanted. Who wouldn't think too hard about it. You fell for his shtick like so many people who came before you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1262
text_en:
¿Sí? 
Ay... then we're both idiots jajaja 
Maybe you DO belong here with us 
Sigh 
My feet hurt 
Mierda, everything hurts

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1263
text_en: What happened wasn't your fault. You were lied to. Yeah, sure - maybe you were a little willingly blind after things started to go wrong. But who can blame you? Hope is a dangerous drug. And he shot you full of it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1264
text_en: You wanted to believe his lies. And so you did. And that's on you. And all the people who got sick because of it? That's also on you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1265
text_en: So of course, you went along with it. Of course, you wanted to believe there was a chance.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1266
text_en: People died. People who won't come back. Because you wanted to believe in a miracle drug hawked by some "old man in some ugly-ass trench coat."

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1267
text_en: But people make mistakes. And people own up to them. And you're here, trying to own up to them. So... I see people trying to do what's right with what they did wrong.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1268
text_en: I would have done the same thing.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1269
text_en: And it's not on me to absolve you of that. Sorry.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo2_1270
text_en: And I don't think a reasonable person can ask for much more than that. I don't think less of you. I see people who failed. But were willing to try again. And I know what that's like. Trust me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1271
text_en:
Sí 
You're right 
We made mistakes 
And I made another one in thinking  THIS could work out

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1272
text_en:
Sí 
You're right 
We made mistakes 
And I made another one in thinking I could trust you with this story

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1273
text_en:
I'm calling it for the day, solecito 
Gracias 
Thanks for listening to me and... 
Not thinking less of us

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo2_1274
text_en:
I'm calling it for the day, friend 
Gracias 
Thanks for listening to me and... 
Not thinking less of us

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_1275
text_en:
Even if it's true... Even if you do leave us someday and don't come back 
I know it would be for the right reasons 
I attacked you and it was wrong

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_1276
text_en: Apology accepted. Thank you, Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieEscape_1277
text_en: You need to learn to stop taking your shit out on other people.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_1278
text_en:
Gracias, pero... 
I... lash out when I get afraid, babas, and that is not your fault

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieEscape_1279
text_en:
Sí, jaja 
You aren't wrong 
I... lash out when I get afraid, babas, and that is not your fault

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1280
text_en:
I suppose there is one good thing 
About being fantasmas trapped for eternity at the edge of Mictlán 
Besides it keeping us from madness

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1281
text_en: Hello to you, too, honey. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1282
text_en: Hello to you, too, Lettie. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1283
text_en: Oh? What's that?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1284
text_en:
Sí, sí 
Yes, yes 
Holiiii solecito jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1285
text_en: BRB [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1286
text_en:
Sí, sí 
Yes, yes 
Hello friend jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1287
text_en:
Mis panquecitos 
My rats 
They won't ever die now, will they?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1288
text_en:
They will live forever with me 
Even if they have an accident, or that gata mutante gets them 
Come new years 
Like nothing happened, ¿no?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1289
text_en: Huh. Yeah. I never thought about that. The loop extends to animals, too.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1290
text_en: And I don't think animals care in the same way people do. Meaning, I don't think it bothers them.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1291
text_en:
Sí 
It means I am always back to training Anita not to eat things she shouldn't jajaja 
And Tláloc will never stop biting

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1292
text_en:
But it means that if I lose them 
They will be back soon 
It is nice to know that I will always have company

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1293
text_en: Uh. Ouch?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1294
text_en:
¡JAJA! 
Lo siento, lo siento 
It's just that 
People have never been constant in my life 
Animals have

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1295
text_en: I suspected you preferred pets to people, but I guess that confirms it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1296
text_en: I assume Anita and Tláloc are the names of two of your rats?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1297
text_en:
Sí, I suppose 
People have never been constant in my life 
Animals have

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1298
text_en:
Mm? 
Have I not told you yet? 
¡Lo siento! Sí 
Vaquero, Anita, Neenah, and Tláloc

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1299
text_en:
I have had pet rats since I was una niña 
They have been a constant in my life 
More than people

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1300
text_en: Yeah, I think I'm starting to figure you out, finally.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1301
text_en: Why do you think that is?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1302
text_en:
¿Ay, sí? 
Go on then 
Tell me why I prefer animals to humans 
Puedes hacer el papel de mi terapeuta

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1303
text_en:
My head is no mystery to me 
I know why, jaja 
Do you?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1304
text_en: I think that you've had a rough run of luck where every time you put your trust in someone, it's been broken. No big sob story. No big trauma. Just a shitty run of luck.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1305
text_en: You're afraid of being abandoned, like how Entrati abandoned his family. So you keep pets because they can't leave you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1306
text_en: You've lost a lot of people in your life to La Flaca. People you've cared about. Pets die, but it's more expected - easier somehow? So you can handle it better.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1307
text_en: You loved someone who betrayed your trust and abandoned you, like how Entrati did to Loid. Pets will never do that to you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1308
text_en:
Mierda, am I so easy to get? 
 Here I thought I would be some great mystery jajaja 
 Sí... that is a lot of it you aren't wrong 
 But like life it's a lot of things all wrapped up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1309
text_en: Loving a pet is easier than loving a person. They just want to be cared for. The relationships are simple - clean - they don't get messy like with people.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1310
text_en: I didn't realize there would be a test.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1311
text_en: Y'know, for someone who makes fun of Amir so much, you really like to play games.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1312
text_en:
My family never left me 
I left them to join the army then the ICR 
No, sometimes I just want a simple kind of love in my life 
From something that won't betray my trust or lie to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1313
text_en:
You clearly have never lost a pet before, babas 
Losing them is like losing part of your own soul 
No, sometimes I just want a simple kind of love in my life 
From something that won't betray my trust or lie to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1314
text_en:
JAJAJA I wish 
Alguna tragedia de amantes condenados 
Something to write plays over 
No, sometimes I just want a simple kind of love in my life 
From something that won't betray my trust or lie to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1315
text_en:
Ay sí 
Tú me entiendes 
Sometimes I just want a simple kind of love in my life 
From something that won't betray my trust or lie to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1316
text_en:
JAJA 
Lo siento, couldn't resist 
I don't get close with people often, wanted to see what you thought 
Did come off bitchy though, jajaa

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1317
text_en:
If you think these are the games I like to play 
You don't know me nearly as well as you think you do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1318
text_en:
There was no big moment 
No name I can hate 
Just a lot of little ones all put together 
Like a necklace of prayer beads for Lua 
One by one they make a string, ¿no?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1319
text_en:
So my rats are just... pure love 
Pure affection 
Nothing messy nothing complicated 
No lies no betrayals no secrets

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1320
text_en: Well, then you've done a bad job of teaching me... ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1321
text_en:
No I keep pets because they are pure love
Pure affection
Nothing messy nothing complicated
No lies no betrayals no secrets

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1322
text_en:
Ay sí
Clearly I have
And I need to fix this mistake

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1323
text_en: I know you just fine. I just don't want to play.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1324
text_en: Yeah, I don't like head games. Have fun with your rats.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1325
text_en: Well, then you've done a bad job of teaching me... ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1326
text_en: Ay equis

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1327
text_en:
I need to get back to work
But now I have something to look forward to

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1328
text_en: Nothing wrong with wanting to come home after a long day and be greeted by creatures that just wants scratches and treats and love

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1329
text_en: I mean, I definitely wouldn't say no to scratches and treats and love...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1330
text_en: Sorry if I'm cramping your style.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1331
text_en:
And knowing that when you love them, they will love you back, no matter what 
No worries about whether they will hurt you Or if you aren't good enough 
Or if you are too tired and sore to deal with their shit

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1332
text_en:
JAJAJA 
Ay, solecito, you make me smile 
But if you want treats you have to be good ¿Sí?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1333
text_en:
Ay, baaaabas 
Not everything is about you 
When my day is long and I am sore and tired I do not want to deal with your shit 
This is EXACTLY why I prefer my panquecitos

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1334
text_en: Yes ma'am. ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1335
text_en: Or... what if I wanted to *not* be good?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1336
text_en: The idea of "dealing with my shit" shouldn't exhaust you more, we're dating.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1337
text_en: Then I'll leave you alone with the creatures you really value.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1338
text_en:
Jajaja, cuidadito 
You are playing with fire 
But I think you know that now

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1339
text_en: Yeah, the last thing I need when I get home after a long day is to be told why I've let someone else down.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1340
text_en: I definitely know how that feels, that's why I love having my pets around.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1341
text_en: I mean, I definitely wouldn't say no to scratches and treats and love... ;)

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1342
text_en:
If you do not understand 
How being with someone can be taxing no matter how much you care about them 
You are too young to be with me 
Go play with Amir or Aoi 
Esto fue un error

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1343
text_en:
Sí please do 
And while you're at it 
You can stay gone babas 
Esto fue un error

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1344
text_en:
JAJAAA me neither 
Cuidadito, or else I will think you are asking me to spend a night with you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1345
text_en:
I need to get back to work 
 But now I have something to look forward to
 Gracias, solecito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1346
text_en:
Ay sí 
You get it 
But it does make life lonely sometimes 
As much as I love them they are not the same

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1347
text_en:
But I suppose I will always have the hex underfoot 
Whether I like it or not jajaja 
Aayyy back to work for me 
Later, buddy

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1348
text_en:
And I'm into some fringe things 
But swinging isn't one, lo siento

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1349
text_en: I mean... you know how I feel.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1350
text_en: What if... I wanted it to be more than a night? [Confess feelings.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1351
text_en: Yikes, sorry, I was just playing around. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1352
text_en:
¿Qué? 
¿En serio?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1353
text_en:
Jajaja ay sí 
Hard to read sarcasm 
Back to work for me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1354
text_en: Before you tell me I'm stupid, or whatever - or that I can't handle you, just wait, and let me talk.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1355
text_en:
Sí I do 
Ayy... this is going to be a mistake... pero... 
Can't bitch about being lonely and then turn away from you 
Do you want to give this a try?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1356
text_en:
Ay sí 
And you know what you said 
Maybe someday I won't be pissed 
Pero today is not that day

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1357
text_en: You're unstoppable. Unbreakable. Unflinching. Nothing seems to slow you down. You're one of the toughest people I've ever met. And -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1358
text_en: Deep down beneath all the layers of armor you've built over yourself, is one of the kindest, most compassionate people I've ever met. But that's not all.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1359
text_en: You're drop-dead gorgeous. You're fiercely intelligent. And you could kick my ass. But that's not the only reasons you've become so important to me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1360
text_en: Let's live dangerously. Yeah. :) [Date Lettie.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1361
text_en: I've changed my mind, sorry. [Do not date Lettie.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1362
text_en:
Encendido, apagado, encendido, apagado 
On, off, on, off 
No more, babas

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1363
text_en:
Jajaja you have no idea 
I need to get back to work 
But now I have something to look forward to 
Gracias, solecito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1364
text_en:
I don't DO compliments, solecito 
Never take them well 
Talk tomorrow, sort this shit out then 
Lo siento

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1365
text_en:
¡Neta, ya cállate! 
I need a second to think 
To breathe 
Can't process when I'm tearing up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1366
text_en: I understand if you don't feel the same way, I get it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1367
text_en: I'm sorry if I upset you...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1368
text_en: Aguántame tantito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1369
text_en: You're one of the kindest, most caring people I've ever met. The way you tend to your animals and the way you'll go out of your way for people makes my heart melt.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1370
text_en: Let's stop to consider how damn gorgeous you are, and how you could absolutely break me like a twig if you wanted to. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1371
text_en: Shut up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1372
text_en: Point is... I care about you, Lettie. A lot. And more than just as friend, and I understand if it isn't mutual, but -

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1373
text_en: You're made of iron. And I know that no matter what they throw at you - Entrati, the Man in the Wall, Viktor and the Scaldra - it doesn't matter. They don't stand a chance.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1374
text_en:
How did you do it, solecito? 
How did you spend all that time alone 
And not go demente

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1375
text_en:
How did you do it, friend? 
How did you spend all that time alone 
And not go demente

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1376
text_en:
How long did you spend in that place where you danced with La Flaca 
Do you even know?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1377
text_en: You mean Duviri? I have no idea... Time lost all meaning.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1378
text_en: You mean Duviri? I wasn't... I mean, I guess I was *technically* alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1379
text_en: I can't chat right now, sorry. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1380
text_en: I kind of blocked it out and went numb. So... I guess I did kind of lose my mind.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1381
text_en: I had people to talk to, even if they weren't... real.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1382
text_en:
Ay sí 
Talking to imaginary friends 
I used to do that when estaba chiquita 
Talking to my panquecitos is much more acceptable jaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1383
text_en:
Sí 
Maybe you did jaja 
But you came back and that gives me hope 
Or at least you are high-functioning crazy jaja 
And I could be happy with that

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1384
text_en: It got *so* lonely, though... even if I had "people" to talk to. It wasn't enough.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1385
text_en:
Sí 
I used to think all I needed was my panquecitos 
A good cup of coffee 
And a day or two off a week 
Now I'm not sure

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1386
text_en: I still talk to myself if I'm not careful. That *really* makes people nervous.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1387
text_en:
¡Jajaja! 
Cuss myself out in Tenochtitlán slang all the time 
Always spooks Arthur 
Thinks I'm gonna stab him or something 
Silly gringo it'd just make a mess

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1388
text_en: What do you mean?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1389
text_en: What's wrong?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1390
text_en:
Used to think I only needed myself 
Suppose I could still be that way if needed 
Not saying what we have isn't wonderful 
It's hard to explain and I am doing poorly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1391
text_en:
I see you and mi hermano Arthur 
It's not jealousy 
I just feel the loneliness suddenly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1392
text_en:
I see you and Aoi 
It's not jealousy 
I just feel the loneliness suddenly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1393
text_en:
I see you and that niño Quincy 
It's not jealousy 
I just feel the loneliness suddenly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1394
text_en:
I see you and that escuincle Amir 
It's not jealousy 
I just feel the loneliness suddenly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1395
text_en:
I see you and la bruja metiche 
It's not jealousy 
I just feel the loneliness suddenly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1396
text_en:
I am happy for you both 
Te lo juro 
He deserves to be with someone finally 
I just... find a sadness in me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1397
text_en:
I am happy for you both 
Te lo juro 
She needs someone to see joy in what she does 
I just... find a sadness in me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1398
text_en:
I am happy for you both 
Te lo juro 
He needs something real in his life 
I just... find a sadness in me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1399
text_en:
I am happy for you both 
Te lo juro 
He needs someone who believes in him 
I just... find a sadness in me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1400
text_en:
I am happy for you both 
Te lo juro 
She needs someone who accepts her as she is 
I just... find a sadness in me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1401
text_en: I know what we've got going on is a start. But I know we're still on a "trial period" in your mind.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1402
text_en: Sometimes when loneliness really gets into you, it doesn't ever let you go, even when you're no longer alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1403
text_en:
Mm that obvious? 
Must be 
Not personal, solecito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1404
text_en: I feel it still, even when I'm sitting around the table with the Hex, laughing and drinking. I'm happy. I'm with everyone. But it's there.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1405
text_en:
Sí, mi corazón 
You understand

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1406
text_en: Like someone removed a kidney or a rib from me once, a long time ago. A hollowness that aches on rainy days.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1407
text_en: I know. Trust is hard for you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1408
text_en: I can be patient.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1409
text_en: But I'm here when you need to shake off the loneliness.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1410
text_en: Point being, no need to feel lonely.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1411
text_en:
Ay, sí, sí... 
I suppose 
Hard to explain

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1412
text_en: Got to go back to work, solecito

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1413
text_en:
I have to go back to work 
But I feel better now 
Gracias, mi corazón...gracias

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1414
text_en: I mean, to be fair, when you get going, you *are* pretty terrifying.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1415
text_en: Right? You'd just be making more work for yourself.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1416
text_en:
JAJAJA 
Aaay, solecito 
This is what I have been missing 
How did you get on without this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1417
text_en:
JAJAJA 
Aaay, friend 
This is what I'm talking about 
How did you get on without this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1418
text_en: Get on without what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1419
text_en: I didn't have a choice.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1420
text_en:
People 
Being with them 
Around them 
Simple shit

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1421
text_en:
Sí... 
And I did I guess 
Still do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1422
text_en:
Loneliness is a sadness that comes like rainstorms 
Or like seasons 
It arrives and leaves a mark that fades 
But it will come again in time

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1423
text_en: You don't have to be alone. You're surrounded by people who care about you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1424
text_en: You never struck me as a poet.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1425
text_en: I... well... you don't *have* to be alone... [Confess Feelings.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1426
text_en:
Sí 
And if you tell anyone I got sappy 
I will gut you like un pescado, ¿entendiste?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1427
text_en:
Even when I'm surrounded by all of you 
My friends and my new family 
Laughing and sharing memories 
There is an ache sometimes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1428
text_en:
Even when I'm surrounded by all of you 
My friends 
Laughing and sharing memories 
There is an ache sometimes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1429
text_en: I think that when loneliness really gets into you, it doesn't ever let you go, even when you're no longer alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1430
text_en: Sounds like you need to cheer up and allow yourself to be happy. Maybe it's depression, have you ever thought of that?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1431
text_en: I feel it still, even when I'm sitting around the table with the Hex, laughing and drinking. I'm happy. I'm with everyone. But it's there.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1432
text_en:
Alway so ready to tell me what to do with myself 
 No, I know those spiders well, and this is not that
 And I've seen that illness many times in myself and in friends
 Army life, remember?
 Seen too many of us go that way

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1433
text_en: Like someone removed a kidney or a rib from me once, a long time ago. A hollowness that aches a little on rainy days.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1434
text_en:
Eating the end of a pistola 
When you couldn't take the nightmares anymore 
No, this small sadness is not like that 
It comes and goes like the rain 
But thanks for the sympathy

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1435
text_en:
Sí, you understand 
Sometimes I can enjoy it almost 
Like a beautiful sadness 
Ay, gracias 
It's nice to know someone understands 
Sometimes you bleed enough and then the bleeding stops

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1436
text_en:
Speaking of 
Someone is bleeding all over and needs my help 
Mierda, back to work I go

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1437
text_en: Loneliness is a sadness that comes and goes in waves. Or like seasons. So it's an easier pain to ignore.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1438
text_en: You don't have to be alone anymore. If you don't want to be. You can let people in for real.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1439
text_en: And I think that when loneliness really gets into you, it doesn't ever let you go, even when you're no longer alone.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1440
text_en: I feel it still, even when I'm sitting around the table with the Hex, laughing and drinking. I'm happy. I'm with everyone. But it's there.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo3_1441
text_en: Like someone removed a kidney or a rib from me once, a long time ago. A hollowness that aches a little on rainy days.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo3_1442
text_en:
Sí, mi corazón, you understand 
Sometimes I can enjoy it almost

Come what may between us
