But now I have to go back to work as always

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo6_1572
text_en:
In seriousness...
Gracias
But I have to go back to work now
Ve

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo6_1573
text_en:
JAJAJA
Wouldn't know
These spiders are not real
Just a name I use for the things in my head that tell me lies

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1574
text_en:
If you are robbed from me 
Who will I have to thank for it? 
What is going to take you away?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1575
text_en: I'm going to say this with all the love and respect in the world - you are *shit* at starting conversations.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1576
text_en: I'm sorry, back up, what are you asking me?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1577
text_en:
¡JAJAJA SÍ! 
I really am, lo siento 
I am just so curious to know that when the future takes you away from me 
What face will it take and why

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1578
text_en:
I am just so curious to know that when the future takes you away from me 
What face will it take and why

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1579
text_en: Even if I did have to leave - who says I wouldn't come back?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1580
text_en:
Maybe you would try 
And maybe you would even succeed 
You are very hard to kill jaja 
But I know soldiers very well, solecito 
And soldiers don't always come back from war 
So tell me why

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1581
text_en: You hate it when I assume things about you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1582
text_en:
Sí I do 
But I also know soldiers very well, solecito 
And you are a soldier whether you like it or not 
When soldiers get called off to "save the world" 
That is what they do 
So tell me why

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1583
text_en: Entrati. I feel like my time chasing him might not be done.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1584
text_en: My Xipe Totec. I know first hand why it *must* be stopped.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1585
text_en: Tau. If that's where Entrati is headed, my Xipe Totec *will* follow him. And it's too important to let them have it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1586
text_en: The Man in the Wall. I know first hand why it *must* be stopped.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1587
text_en: Tau. If that's where Entrati is headed, The Man in the Wall. *will* follow him. And it's too important to let them have it.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1588
text_en: I'm NEVER leaving. End of story.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1589
text_en:
Do I need more reasons to hate that cabrón 
Now you give me one more 
But he will ruin more places more lives 
Like he's ruined so many others

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1590
text_en:
Your story with the skinned god of the Void... sí 
I fear it may not be over 
And who am I to think I am important enough to stand in the way of it

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1591
text_en:
Didn't think you were that naive 
This thing between us is clearly a mistake, babas 
You are too young for me I think 
If you can't understand the reality of all this

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1592
text_en:
Ay, sí 
If it is not one of us to put a bullet in his skull It should be you 
And I hope that once you go and make him pay 
You will come back to us 
And to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1593
text_en:
Maybe when you finally defeat this skinned god of yours 
You won't forget about us back here in this cuchitril 
You will come back to us 
And to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1594
text_en:
This Tau This is where the... sentients were sent ¿no? 
This fake race made by fake gods the orokin

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1595
text_en:
Tell me of this Tau 
What is it 
Tell me why it would take you from me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1596
text_en: Tau is a planet in another solar system, where the Orokin sent a synthetic race they created to terraform it for us.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1597
text_en: The race were called Sentients. But the Sentients turned on the Orokin. Came back here and waged war on them.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1598
text_en: And it was that war that drove the Orokin to create the infestation - and warframes - in the first place. To fight the Sentients.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1599
text_en:
So if it were not for this Tau and these Sentients 
This fake race made by these fake gods the orokin 
None of these pendejadas would have ever happened

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1600
text_en: Yeah, but then we never would have met. Or started dating. So... small upside?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1601
text_en: Basically.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1602
text_en:
Jajaja sí 
Small upside 
But why? 
Why is this place so important that it will take you from me some day

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1603
text_en:
But why? 
Why is this place so important that it will take you from me some day

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1604
text_en: I'm not sure. But if Entrati *and* the Man in the Wall are headed there... it has to be important.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1605
text_en: It was the only hope for humanity's survival. Might still be, honestly.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1606
text_en: I'm not sure. But the Sentients have said some cryptic things.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1607
text_en:
Sí 
And I hope that once you go and make him pay 
You will come back to us 
And to me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1608
text_en:
Ay no 
So we can ruin a second planet like this one 
I think I agree with the sentients jajaja 
Besides we seem to have done just fine in space, ¿no?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1609
text_en: "All is silent and calm, hushed and empty is the womb of the sky."

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1610
text_en:
¿Cómo qué? 
¿Like what?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1611
text_en: "Merely framed Merely shaped they are called. There was no their mother, there was no their father."

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1612
text_en: Fair enough. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1613
text_en: Might want to wait to meet the future before you make that call.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1614
text_en: I promise that IF I do go, I WILL come back.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1615
text_en: All I can do is promise to try as hard as I possibly can.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1616
text_en:
How many soldaditos have made that promise 
And died in a ditch an hour later 
Aay but I know you mean it when you say it 
You will try

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1617
text_en:
That is a promise I can trust 
That is a promise I believe 
Gracias, mi corazón

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1618
text_en:
Back to work for me 
Again as always 
Never ending... never will

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1619
text_en:
¡¿QUÉ?! 
WHAT DID YOU JUST SAY?! 
WAIT WAIT WAIT WAIT WAIT WAIT

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1620
text_en:
¿POR QUÉ? why are creatures from the far future quoting ¿a los PUEBLOS ANTIGUOS? 
¿Qué chingados está pasando ahora?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1621
text_en: Um. I'm sorry. What? What were they quoting?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1622
text_en: Lettie you've lost me again. Back up.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1623
text_en:
AGGHHHH this makes NO SENSE 
Those words are the words of the ancient people of Chichén Itzá. WHERE DID YOU GET THEM?!

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1624
text_en:
THOSE ARE FROM A SACRED TEXT OF LOS PUEBLOS ANTIGUOS 
"¡¿CÓMO Y POR QUÉ!?"

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1625
text_en: I - I don't - I don't know. I have no clue. I'd only be guessing.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo7_1626
text_en: Time travel...?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1627
text_en:
I do not drink 
But if I did now would be the time 
Aaayyyy this nonsense gets worse and worse every day

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo7_1628
text_en:
I... need to go sit down, mi corazón 
Do not talk to me of the future for a while, ¿Sí? 
Think I've had enough of it for a long time 
Gives me a damn headache

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1629
text_en:
Mi corazón 
I have a confession

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1630
text_en:
Mi solecito 
I have a confession

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1631
text_en:
Friend 
I have a confession

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1632
text_en: Yeah, babe?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1633
text_en: What's up, L?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1634
text_en: Uh oh...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1635
text_en: I'm sorry, Kalymos is chewing on the power cord, and - [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1636
text_en: Jajaja hear me out

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1637
text_en:
When you came here 
I knew you were going to be trouble 
A new impossible problem to add to our growing pile of mierda to deal with

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1638
text_en: Gee, thanks.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1639
text_en: I mean... sure, but...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1640
text_en:
Then things went from bad to worse 
From shit to more shit 
As the nightmare grew darker 
And ANYONE with half a brain would have run back to the future

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1641
text_en:
But you didn't 
You stayed for some stupid reason 
You stayed with us and you fought and you helped us put ourselves back together

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1642
text_en:
Ay, Lua, sálvame 
I still do NOT know why 
You had no reason to stay for strangers

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1643
text_en: I have seen the face of your Xipe Totec and I would have run to the farthest corner and prayed it did not wear mine next

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1644
text_en:
I would have called the Cavia my family and stayed with them instead 
They seem FAR less broken and far more deserving of love

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1645
text_en:
But you DID stay 
And for me... much more than that... 
Which is what I am trying to say, mi corazón

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1646
text_en:
But you DID stay 
And had the audacity to say you had feelings for me jajaja

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1647
text_en:
But you DID stay 
And for me I find a dear friend I never would have expected 
One I do not know how I survived without

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1648
text_en:
With you around... we are not fantasmas 
Without you we would be lost and adrift 
We would be sleepwalking through our deaths again and again, meaningless and empty 
At the edge of Mictlán

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1649
text_en:
But you made us into a new family 
Even la bruja y yo jajaja 
And I love them more than I can say 
And it is all thanks to you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1650
text_en:
But you showed me why the moments matter most 
The kindness and love we show each other 
That is why we are here 
And it is all thanks to you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1651
text_en:
But you showed me why it does not matter 
Because it is the company we keep not our destination 
It is the trust, the love, and the kindness we share 
And it is all thanks to you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1652
text_en:
I hate all this sappy feely shit 
Drives me crazy 
I'm bad at it 
So I'm going to wrap this up

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1653
text_en: Lol. You're doing great.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1654
text_en: I don't know, I'm enjoying Sweet Lettie.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank6Convo1_1655
text_en: Hmm? I dozed off again.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1656
text_en:
Don't get used to it, mi corazón 
I'll still kick your ass 
Ay, here goes...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1657
text_en:
Don't get used to it, solecito 
I'll still kick your ass 
Point is, I've gotten used to having you underfoot 
I like having you around

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1658
text_en:
Don't get used to it 
I'll still kick your ass 
Point is, I've gotten used to having you underfoot 
I like having you around

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1659
text_en:
Te amo, mi corazón 
I love you, my heart

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1660
text_en:
Me importas mucho 
I care about you a great deal 
And I rely on you in ways I don't rely on anyone else 
I trust you and that is not something I do lightly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1661
text_en:
Your friendship is so valuable to me 
And I rely on you in ways I don't rely on anyone else 
I trust you and that is not something I do lightly

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank6Convo1_1662
text_en:
Here's to us, solecito 
And here is to the future 
Filled with fantasmas and endless futures and gods and demons as they may be 
We have each other 
And that is plenty good enough

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank2Convo3_1689
text_en: Transference will finally be good for something, eh

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo2_1676
text_en: Tú te lo pierdes

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1677
text_en: Yikes, sorry, I was just playing around. lol

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1678
text_en:
Jajaja ay sí 
Hard to read sarcasm 
Back to work for me

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank5Convo4_1679
text_en: Darn. Well, there goes that fantasy.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank5Convo4_1680
text_en:
Sí 
Sorry to disappoint

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1681
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1682
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1683
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1684
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1685
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank4Convo8_1686
text_en: And?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_1692
text_en: Dying on endless repeat does that to you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_1693
text_en: Dying on endless repeat does that to you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_1694
text_en: Dying on endless repeat does that to you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieRank1Convo4_1695
text_en: Dying on endless repeat does that to you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieRank1Convo4_1696
text_en:
But I am curious
This kingdom of death of yours
Tell me more

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1697
text_en:
Hey
Quincy came to talk to me
Said you wanted to talk?
¿Qué pasó?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1698
text_en: I just... wanted to say sorry, Lettie. That's all.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1699
text_en: I... well. I have feelings for you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1700
text_en: He must have been mistaken. [End.]

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1701
text_en: Lárgate de aquí, cabrón

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1708
text_en:
JAJA Sí, that's what he said
I didn't believe him at first
But now I'm impressed that you've got him working for you, huh?
Ay, there I go again...

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1709
text_en:
You just want to apologize and I'm making it hard for you
All right
Apology accepted

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1702
text_en:
You had your chance
And it didn't go so well, did it?
But... aaaay, sí...
Hard to admit that I miss you

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1703
text_en:
You kept this to yourself the whole time?
¿Por qué?
I am right here

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1704
text_en: Couldn't tell you.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1705
text_en: No idea.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1706
text_en:
Well...
Whatever
You want to do this?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1710
text_en:
He *also* said you wanted to give things a shot with me
Us
A thing, together
¿Verdad?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1707
text_en: You want to give this another try?

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1711
text_en: Yeah. :) I would.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1712
text_en:
Sí, okay then
Let's get on with it, then
¡Va!, there's work to do

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieQuincyWingman_1713
text_en: Actually, never mind.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieQuincyWingman_1714
text_en:
¿Babas?
Sometimes, I want to smack you
This is one of those times

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/TxtLettie_LettieBirthdayConvo2_1715
text_en:
Hah!
I wish
I do get off early, though. Good enough for me.

name: /Lotus/Language/1999Texting/LettieRomance/Choice_LettieBirthdayConvo3_1719
text_en: Hey! Have any fun plans for your birthday? Like going to bed early?
